Mai aiki daga nesa ko akasin haka, ba ka da wani dalili na rashin motsa jiki. Kuma ga dalili kamar haka Mahimman abubuwan lura Cututttukan da ba a dauka (NCDs), wanda suka haɗa da cutukan zuciya, daji, cututtukan numfashi, da kuma cutar suga, su ne kan gaba wajen haifar da mace-mace a duniya kuma barazana mai tasowa a kiwon lafiya. Duk da haka, yawan motsa jiki zai taimakawa lafiyar zuciya, ƙarfin ƙwanji, da kuma lanƙwasa jiki a yayin da yake rage Haɗarin yawan ƙiba, ciwon suga, da kuma wasu cutuka masu tsanani. Kama daga abin da ya shafi manhajar motsa jiki zuwa ga samar da abubuwan motsa jiki a yanar gizo da kuma cikin al’umma, fasaha tana sanya motsa jiki ya zama cikin sauƙin samu, da dagewa da inganci fiye da koyaushe. Cutututtukan da ba a ɗauka (NCDs), wanda suka haɗa da cutukan zuciya, daji, cutututtukan numfashi, da kuma ciwon suga, su ne kan gaba wajen haifar da mace-mace a duniya kuma barazana mai tasowa a kiwon lafiya. A shekara 2010, Ƙungiyar Lafiya ta Duniya WHO) ta yi hasashen cewa za a samu ƙari mai yawan gaske na mace-mace a nahiyar Afiriƙa daga cututtukan da ba a ɗauka a fiye da shekaru goma masu zuwa. A cewar 2022 fact sheet, mutane miliyan 17 ne suke mutuwa dalilin NCD kafin su cika shekaru 70 a kowacce shekara. Wannan mutuwar wurin tana daukan kaso 86% na mutuwa a ƙasashen masu ƙaramin ƙarfin ko madaidaici sannan kuma kaso 77% na mace-macen da suka danganci Cututtukan da ba a Ɗauka suna faruwa ne a can. Abun takaici, a 2023, cututtukan da ba a ɗauka za su kasance kan gaba wajen mace-mace a a Yankin Afirka Kudu da Sahara, har su zarce cututtukan da ake ɗauka, da na haihuwa, na jarirai, da kuma na gina jiki (CMNN). Manhajojin waya, EHRs, da kuma sauran kayayyaki na fasaha da suke taimakawa mutanen Afirka wajen kulawa da kuma rigakafin cututtuka Me ya sa aka samu ƙaruwar NCDs a Afirka? Dalilai da dama, wanda ya haɗa da yawan tsofaffi, rashin wadatar kayan aikin kiwon lafiya, da kuma rashin samuwar hanyar gane cuta da wuri, rigakafi, da kuma magani, su ne suka samar da ƙkaruwar NCDs a Afirka. Bayan haka, talauci da rashin daidaito a Afirka mafi yawan lokuta suna haifar da rashin samun zaɓi ga abinci mai ƙara lafiya, wuraren motsa jiki wanda ba su da haɗari, da kuma kiwon lafiya mai inganci, wanda hakan yasa rigakafin NCD da kuma magance shi ya zama abu mai matuƙar wahala. Yawaitar zamanantarwa a Afirka ta sanya tsarin rayuwa da sauyin abinci, ta yadda mtane da yawa suke cin kayan da aka sarrafa mai yawan gishiri, suga, da kuma kitse mara amfani. Cigaban fasaha ma ya haifar da ƙaruwar yin rayuwar zama waje ɗaya kuma ya haifar da raguwar ayyukan motsa jiki. Duk da haka, yawan motsa jiki zai iya ƙara lafiyar zuciya, ƙarfin kwanji, da kuma lanƙwasa jiki ya kuma rage haɗarin ƙiba mai yawa, ciwon suga, da kuma sauran cututtuka masu haɗari. Amma kafin mu cigaba, dole ne mu fahimci bambanci tsakanin ayyukan jiki da kuma motsa jiki. Mene ne bambanci tsakanin ayyukan jiki da kuma motsa jiki? Kamar yadda WHO ta ce, ayyukan jiki sun haɗa da dukkan motsin ƙashi da tsoka wanda yake buƙatar ƙarfi, da ya haɗa har wanda ake yi yayin aiki, wasa, yin ayyukan gida, tafiye-tafiye, da kuma shiga gasar wasanni. Wannan yana nuna yadda rayuwar zama waje ɗaya take rage motsa jiki, wanda hakan yake ƙara yawan barazanar samun NCD a tare da kai. A ranar mako, a misali, ina shafe kusan sa’o’i takwas a kwamfutata nakan tashi ne kawai idan zan ci abinci ko kuma zan shiga banɗaki. Haɗarin kiwon lafiya da ba a kauce masa wanda samar da fasaha ta haifar. Saboda ina shafe aƙalla sa’o’i shida a kowacce rana a zaune ko a kwance ba tare da yin wasu ayyuka da zan motsa jiki ba, ina rayuwa ne ta zama waje ɗaya. Tsahon wanne lokaci kake ɗauka kana aiki a ofishinka idan ba ka yin aiki daga gida? Zama a cikin mota ko bas ba ya daga cikin aikin motsa jiki. Sai dai idan kana tafiya da ƙafa ne ko kuma kana tuƙa keke zuwa wajen aiki, ya kamata ka yi aikin motsa jiki sosai. Duk mako, WHO tana shawartar manya ‘yan shekaru tsakanin 18 da 64 da su dinga yin aikin motsa jiki matsakaici aƙalla na mintuna 150, aikin motsa jiki mai yawa aƙalla na mintuna 75, ko kuma wanda ya haɗa duka biyun a daidaito. Manya kuma su yi aikin motsa jiki madaidaici aƙalla na mintuna 300 duk sati, ko kuma wanda ya kusan haka, domin ƙarin samun lafiya. Kuma za su iya ware kwana biyu ko fiye a cikin sati domin motsa jiki wanda ya danganci ƙwanji. Sannan kuma, ko da kana yin aiki ne daga gida ko kuma kana aikin ƙarfe 9-5, sanya aikin motsa jiki a ciki zai taimaka maka a ranakun aikinka. “Yin ayyukan motsa jiki” da kuma “motsa jiki” ba a cancanza su saboda motsa jiki yana nufin aikin da za ayi da jiki wanda aka tsara, aka shirya, kuma ake yinsa akai-akai tare da cim ma buri, kamar ƙara ƙarfin ƙwanji, ƙara lafiyar zuciya, ko rage ƙiba. Me ya sa motsa jiki yake da mahimmanci? Bincike ya nuna cewa yawan motsa jiki na sa tsahon rayuwa. Wani bincike na Jami’ar Harvard ya nuna cewa mutanen da suke mots jiki wanda aka yarda da shi madaidaici suna rage barazanar mutuwarsu da wuri da kashi 21%. Ga kowanne bincike, motsa jiki akai-akai yana ƙara tsahon ran mutum da shekaru uku zuwa biyar. Yawan motsa jiki yana ƙara lafiyar zuciya, da ƙarfin ƙashi da tsoka, yana ƙara lanƙwasar jiki sannan ya rage haɗarin kamuwa da cututtuka masu girma. Yin gudu ko tuƙa keke, a misali, yana taimakawa wajen ƙara lafiyar zuciya da huhu, wanda zai rage haɗarin ciwon zuciya da sauran cututtukan masu Haɗari. Motsa jiki da yake ƙara ƙarfin ƙashi da tsoka, kamar ɗaga kayan nauyi ko danƙo, kan iya rage haɗarin osteoporosis. Shin ka taɓa motsa jiki ka ji ka samu nutsuwa ka cire duk gajiya? Na taɓa, kuma motsa jiki ya tabbadar da ƙarin lafiyar ƙwaƙwalwa ta hanyar cire gajiya, da muwa, rashin nutsuwa da kuma sauran alamomin ciwon damuwa. Kuma yana taimakwa wajen sanya farin ciki da ƙara tunani mai amfani. A misali, sanya yoga ko gyaran tunani a cikin ayyukan motsa jiki zai taimaka wajen rage gajiya da kuma damuwa. Yawan motsa jiki zai iya rage haɗarin ƙiba ta hanyar rage kitse da kuma ƙara ƙarfin tsoka. Ƙananun motsa jiki kamar tafiya ko iyo na iya narkar da kitse sannan kuma ya taimaka wajen ƙara ƙarfin tsoka, wanda hakan zai sa kitse ya narke ko da kana hutawa ne. Saboda suna samun barci mafi kyau kuma mafi tsaho, mutanen da suke yawan motsa jiki sun fi samun kuzari da hutu. A misali, motsa jiki mara ƙarfi, kamar yoga ko tafiya, zai iya inganta maka barcinka, sannan kuma motsa jiki mai ƙarfi, wanda ya haɗa ɗaga kayan ƙarfi ko gudu, zai iya sanya barcinka ya yi tsaho. Duk da waɗannan amfanin, mutane da dama ba sa motsa jiki saboda ayyukansu na da yawa da kuma hidimar iyali, ayyukan yi, da sauran ayyuka. Wasu kuma ba su da halin motsa jikin, wasu ba su da damar samun kayan motsa jiki, gurin motsa jiki, da sauran abubuwan amfani da za su iya taimakawa wajen motsa jiki. Sannan kuma, wasu suna ƙoƙarin samun ƙwarin guiwa, musamman idan ba sa jin daɗin yi ko kuma ba su ga sakamako da wuri ba. Wasu kuma ba sa sanin yadda ya dace su motsa jiki ko susan amfanin motsa jikin. Tsananin ciwo da kuma matsalar motsi su ne biyu daga cikin dalilan da suke sanyawa mots jiki ya zama mai wahala ko mara daɗi. Bayan kaha, wasu suna samun rashin nutsuwa ko rashin yarda da kai yayin da suke motsa jiki a gaban mutane, wanda yakan hana su farawa ko ƙin cigaba da yin motsa jikin. Abun sha’awa, fasaha na taimakawa wajen gyara matsalolin motsa jiki da kuma tallata ingantacciyar rayuwa. Don haka yanzu, babu wani dalili da zai hana ka motsa jiki. A shekarun yanzu, fasaha ta canja ɗa yawa daga al’amuran rayuwarmu, wanda ya haɗa da yadda muke fuskantar ayyukanmu na motsa jiki da kyautata sura. Ƙari a kan haka, an samu ƙaruwar ra’ayoyi a kan motsa jiki da kyautata sura a Afirka saboda mutane da dama sun san amfanin yawan motsa jiki ga lafiyar jikinsu da ƙwaƙwalwarsu. Hari la yau, fasaha ta bunƙasa da sauri, wanda hakan ya yi amfani ga yawaitar motsa jiki a Afirka. Yana taka muhimmiyar rawa wajen canja tunanin mutane wajen motsa jiki da kyautata sura. Amma ta yaya? tsare-tsaren motsa jiki na karan kai Mutane za su iya samun tsare-tsaren motsa jiki na karan kansu wanda zai dace da buƙatarsu da manufarsu. Manhajojin motsa jiki da kayan sawarsu kan iya nemo awo na kiwon lafiya, wanda ya haɗa da gudun zuciya, tsarin barci, da matakan da aka ɗauka, sannan ya yi amfani da wannan bayanan domin samar da tsarin motsa jiki na karan kai. Wasu daga cikin wayoyin zamani, kamar Samsung suna yin haka. Ba ka buƙatar sake sauke wata manhajar. Kawai ka ziyarci ”Samsung Health” domin fara kula da kiwon lafiyarka. Kuma, Apple Fitness+ yana nan a manhajar motsa jiki idan kana da wayar iPhone, iPad, ko Apple TV. Na’urorin bibiyar lafiyar jiki kamar fitness bands da kuma smatwatches suna ƙara wadatuwa a Afirka. Apple Watch na ɗaya daga cikin misalin. Za kuma ka iya sauke wasu manhajojin, kamar Google Fit idan wayarka ta zamani ba ta da su tun farko. Za ka iya amfani da wannan domin samun ƙwarin guiwa, ka dinga bibiyar matakin motsa jikinka, ka tsara motsa jiki mai amfani. Za ka iya samar da tsarin motsa jikinka daidai da buƙatarka ta wannan tsare-tasren a mabambanta yanayi, wanda ya haɗa da matakin motsa jiki, shekaru, da kuma lafiya. Tunƙarar motsa jiki na karan kai zai iya taimaka maka wajen samun sakamako mai kyau kuma ya tabbatar da motsa jiki mara haɗari kuma mai amfani. Ajujuwan yanar gizo da kuma bayanai. Annobar COVID-19, wanda ta haddasa rufe wararen motsa jiki na dole da wajen bayar da kayan motsa jiki, na ɗaya daga cikin dalilan da suka faɗaɗa azuzuwan motsa jiki na yanar gizo da kuma samar da da kayan buƙata a nahiyar. Afirka a yanzu tana samun damar shiga azuzuwan motsa jiki na yanar gizo wanda ƙwararru suke koyarwa a duniya sakamakon dandalin yanar gizo da kuma bidiyo na manhajoji. Saboda yanzu mutane da dama za su iya shiga azuzuwan koyar da motsa jiki a wajen mazauninsu, mutane da dama suna samun bayanai na motsa jiki, wanda hakan ya sa aka bar buƙatuwa zuwa ga mai koyar da motsa jiki, wanda zai iya cin kuɗi. Mutanen Afirka za su iya samun tsarin motsa jiki, bidiyon motsa jiki, da kuma shawarwarin motsa jiki ta wannan manhajar, yanar gizo, da kuma dandalin sada zumunta, wanda yake ba su damar sanin abunci mai gina jiki, da hanyoyi mabambanta na motsa jiki, da kuma kiwon lafiya na baiɗaya da lafiya. A dalilin yawaitar samuwar wayar zamani da kuma yanar gizo a nahiyar, wannan bayanin yana taimaka musu wajen yanke hukunci game da manufarsu ta motsa jiki da kuma dabaru. Saboda haka, ba sai ka je gidan motsa jiki ba kafin ka motsa jiki. YouTube na da bayanai da dama, wanda ya haɗa dabidiyo na kowanne irin motsa jiki. Za ka iya yi kafin ka tafi zuwa aiki ko bayan ka dawo. Ka samu kwarin guiwa daga awon lafiyarka. Ƙari a kan haka, za ka iya neman kayan aiki ta neman mahimman kalmomi kamar”motsa jiki,”aerobics,” da kuma “workout” a kowanne dandalin sada zumunta. Al’umomin yanar gizo Fasaha ta taimaka wajen cigaban al’aummar motsa jiki ta yanar gizo a Afirka. Masu ƙaunar motsa jiki a yanzu za su iya jonawa, musanyar dabaru, da kuma taimakon juna a tafiyarsu ta motsa jiki a dandalin sada zumunta, al’ummar yanar gizo, da wuraren da aka ware domin motsa jiki. Waɗannan al’ummar yanar gizon suna bayar da ƙwarin guiwa, ƙarfafawa, da sakamako, wanda zai iya zama abu mai girma wajen tabbatar da tsarin motsa jiki. Al’ummar motsa jiki ta yanar gizo na sanyawa ka ji cewa ka dace a wajen ta hanyar samar da waje mai nutsuwa ta yadda mutane za su iya taimakon juna, musayar cigaba, da kuma aiki cikin wahala. Kayan motsa jiki na gida. Fasaha ta sauƙaƙawa mutane da dama don samar da wajen motsa jikinsu a cikin gida da kayan motsa jiki masu sauƙin kuɗi. A yanzu da akwai zaɓi da dama ga mutane domin su motsa jiki a cikin gidajensu, wanda ya ƙunshi robar atisaye zuwa injinan motsa jiki masu sauƙin mallaka. Yana taimakawa wanda ba su da wajen motsa jiki ko guraren koyar da motsa jiki a inda suke. Da akwai yawaitar zaɓin kayan motsa jiki da aka ƙera musamman domin bukatar mutanen Afirka da kuma kasafinsu, wanda ya kama daga kayan motsa jiki masu sauƙin siye da kuma kayan sa wa na motsa jiki na cikin gida. Ya danganta da irin motsa jikinka, kayan aikinka zai iya kunsar yoga ko taɓarmar motsa jiki, robar atisaye da yake zuwa a awo daban daban, da bal ɗin roba ta atisaye da bencin hawa da sauka na atisaye da wilin atisaye faya-fayan atisaye ko igiyar tsalle. Idan kana tunani ko ba ka san ta yadda za ka fara ba, za ka iya kallon kayan amfani na yanar gizo yayin da kake amfani da kayan motsa jikinka. Yadda za ka samar da tsarin motsa jiki Samar da tsarin motsa jiki da za ka iya tsayawa akai yana da wahala, amma da tsari mai kyau, yana iya kasancewa. Ga wasu dabaru nan. Ka duba matakin motsa jikinka Neman matakin motsa jikinka na lokacin shi ne babban mataki na farko na masar da tsarin motsa jiki domin cim ma manufarka da buƙatarka. Za ka iya sanin matsayin motsa jikinka ta waɗannan hanyoyin: Lura da yanayin lafiyarka yayin da kake motsa jiki hanya ce ta gane juriyar zuciyarka. Sanya na’urar kula da gudun zuciya ko amfani da na’urar bibiyar motsa jiki zai taimake ka wajen sanin gudun zuciyarka. Za ka iya yin gudu na minti 12 a ɓangaren yin gwajin gudun minti 12 domin auna juriyar zuciyarka. Za ka iya auna matakin ƙarfin ƙwanjinka ta yin motsa jikin push-ups, sit-ups, ko squats da kuma ƙirga maimaici nawa za ka iya yi. Domin gwada juriyar ƙwanjinka, ka yi motsa jiki, wanda ya haɗa da, tsayuwa a kan guiwar hannaye da jingina da bango da lanƙwasa ƙafa, sai ka ƙirga har izuwa yaushe ne za ka iya tsayawa. Domin auna lanƙwasar jiki, ka zauna a ƙasa tare da ƙafafunka a miƙe a gabanka ka kuma miƙa hannunka gaba domin yin gwajin sit-and-reach. Ka yi amfani abubuwa kamar na'urar auna kitse domin auna kason kitsen da yake jikinka don sanin abin da jikinka ya ƙunsa. Za ka iya zaƙulo gabaki ɗayan abin da ya danganci lafiyarka da haɗarin kamuwa da cututtuka masu haɗari ta yin amfani da ma’aunai kamar waist circumference ko body mass index (BMI). Za ka iya gwada motsa jiki kamar tsayuwa a kan ƙafa ɗaya yayin da idanuwanka suke a rufe ko tafiya da ƙafa a layi miƙaƙƙe domin gwada balas ɗinka da kuma daidaituwa. A tsara manufa ta gaske Tsara manufar da za a iya cim ma na zuwa ne bayan an duba matsayin motsa jiki na kusa. Manufofinka su zama na ƙalubalanta amma kuma wanda za a iya aikatawa a cikin lokacin da ya kamata. Ka samar da tsari madaidaici ka kuma fara a sannu. Akwai wahala wajen zabar motsa jiki da zai tafi da dabarunka, don haka ka tsara motsa jikinka kuma ka shigar da su cikin ayyukanka na rana ko mako. Ka zaɓi lokacin da ya dace da kai. Yana da muhimmanci a fara a hankali sannan a bunƙasa zuwa babban mataki mai yawa zuwa wani lokaci. Zai sanya ya zamo da sauƙin kasancewa a cikin tsarin motsa jikinka kuma ya kiyaye samun rauni. Ka haɗa motsa jikinka kuma ka dinga bibiyar cigabanka. Yana da wahala ka banbanta motsa jikinka domin kaucewa kaɗaici da kuma rashin samun sakamako. A gwada sabbabin motsa jiki, a ƙara yawansa, ko a ƙara masa wasu ayyukan. Za ka iya lura da cigabanka ta hanyar ajiye sakamakon motsa jikinka da kuma lura da matakin motsa jikinka. Yin hakan zai sanya kwarin guiwarka ya ƙaru.
TECNO ta sake bunƙasa fasaha a wayar hannu da ƙayataccen CAMON 20 Doddle Design! Don bunƙasa cigaban CAMON 19 Mondrian edition, TECHNO ta sake gabatar da wata wayar mai matuƙar ƙayatarwa da cigaba, CAMON 20 Doodle Edition tare da Android. Wannan karon, murfin bayan yana zuwa ne a bayyane tare da ƙayataccen zanen Doodle din, yayin da doodles din ke rawa a cikin inuwa yana barin kyau da inganci duk inda ka je. Zane ne na musamman wanda aka yi domin faɗaɗa yadda muke ganin zane a wayoyin hannu. Tare da CAMON 20 Doddle Edition ta aka gabatar da Android, doodling ya wuce a kira shi da tsari kawai na bayyanar da halin da ake ciki; ya zama wata babbar ƙwarewa da ta haɗa zane da fasaha. Murfin bayan ya ƙawatu da zanen Doodle mai haske a wajen da yake da duhu wanda ya ƙayatu da ɗaukar hankali, wanda yake haska tattaunawa kuma yake jan hankali. Kowanne tsari na zanen Doodle ɗin an cika shi da fasaha da ƙirƙira, wanda hakan ya sa CAMON 20 Doodle Edition din ya kasance ba wai na’aura kawai ba amma wata matattarar samun damarmaki. Amma dabon bai kare a nan ba. Fiye da fasahar zanenta, TECHNO CAMON 20 Doodle Edition yana samar da ilimi mai sauƙi kuma mai ƙarfi ga masu amfani da shi. Google Andoid 19 ya ɗauki nauyin shi, TECNO CANON 20 Doodle Edition yana bunƙasa karkon batiri 5000mAh, wanda zai bayar da wuta gaba ɗayan rana, da kuma caja mai saurin 33W wanda zai mayar masa wautar nan da nan. Na’ura ce da take cikin shiri domin tafiya da fasaharka da kuma ƙwarin guiwa a rana baki ɗaya. Manajan tallatawa TECHNO, Thompson Ani, y ace, “Ita CAMON 20 Doodle Edition ba wai kawai waya bace; dandaline na bayyana abin da yake zuciyar mutum. Yana wakiltar dagewarmu ta ƙirƙira da samarwa, wanda yake rufe nisan da ke tsakanin zane da fasaha ta hanya ta musamman.” A ƙarƙashin rumfar, an cika CANON 20 Doodle Edition da abubuwan nunawa masu matuƙar burgewa da amfani domin ya tafi daidai da yanayin rayuwarka. Yana tabbatar da ƙwarewa mara yankewa ga mai amfani da ita, ta mayar da shi abokin tafiyar da za a dogara da shi domin buɗe ido a kullum. Masu ƙaunar ɗaukar hoto za su yi farin ciki da kyakkayawar kyamarar wadda take da abun hana girgiza, tare da tabbatar da cewa kowanne hoto ya yi kyau kuma ya tsaya. Ko a lokacin da ake fuskantar barazanar walƙiya, kyamarar mai sauƙin haske tana bayar da hotuna masu kyau wanda za su burge masu fasahar zane. Ka tuna, bai sai ka fasa banki ba kafin ka shiga wannan buɗe idon mai ƙayatarwa ba, saboda da biyan 30%, za ka iya mallakar CANON 20 Doodle Edition ko kuma kowanne daga ire-iren CANON 20 din. Abin da za ka yi kawai shi ne ka shiga ko wanne irin ofishin TECHNO da aka yarda da shi ka siya wayar ta hanyar amfani da EasyBuy tare da 0% na kuɗin ruwa. Kada ka saki jiki, ka je ka siya ka fara zanen. Ka dinga dubawa saboda TECNO tana yin tattaki da mu zuwa wajen da zane yake zama gaske tare da CAMON 20 Doodle Edition. Ku bibiyi TECHNO a manhajar Facebook, Instagram da kuma Twitter domin cigaba na kusa kuma a zama cikin shiri domin yin tattakin buɗe ido na zane da fasaha irin wanda ba a taɓa gani ba!
Duke & ICANBOI sun yi taron SME Bootcamp domin bunƙasa masu kasuwanci fiye da 100. Legas, cibiyar tattalin arzikin Nijeriya waje ne na masu ƙanana da matsakaicin kasuwanci (SME) a Nijeriya kuma ƙasa ce da take saurin samun canje-canje, yawan dokoki da kuma rashin sanin makamar aiki wani lokacin wajen neman mafita. SME Bootcamp 1.0 Initiative ya maida hankali ne wajen gyara matsalolin tafiyar da sabon kasuwanci ko wanda ake yinsa a lokacin a Legas Nijeriya ta hanyar samarwa da masu sabo ko tsohon kasuwanci kayan buƙata da damarmaki domin tabbatar da kasuwancinsu a kasuwar da take cike da abokan gasa na kasuwanci a koda yaushe. Duke Sell, tare da haɗin guiwar ICANBOI, da Lagos State Employment Trust Fund (LSETF), Institute of Chartered Accountants of Nigeria (ICAN) da kuma Bank of Industry (BOI), Jobtech Alliance, da Salad Afirka za su tattara sababbin SME na zamani don samarwa da masu sana’ar hannu da kasuwanci ilimi, horo, da kuma damarmaki domin bunƙasa da cigaban kasuwancinsu. An yi wa bootcamp ɗin taken “An SME Guide to Starting and Growing Your Business” wanda za a gudanar da shi a dandalin ICANBOI Innovation wanda yake a tsakiyar Yaba, Legas. Bootcamp ɗin ya tanadarwa wanda suka shiga tsarin, masu sabo da tsohon kasuwanci damarmaki na samun horo, kayan amfani da damarmaki da ake buƙata domin rage wahalar farawa ko bunƙasa kasuwanci a matsayinka na mai sana’a a Legas. Rana: Agusta 26 2023 (Asabar) Lokaci: karfe 10 na safe Wuri: ICANBOI Innovation Hub 5th Floor, 83 Murtala Mohammed Way, Ebute-Metta, Lagos. ME YA SA ZA A HALARTA? Samun horo da damarmaki don cigaba Samun tallafin kudi da kayan amfani Domin samun haɗuwa da mutane da ƙungiyoyi Bootcamp ɗin kyauta ne!, Ka je bit./SMEBizClinic domin samun wajen zama. Yin rijista dole ne. Game da mu Dukesell Duke wani dandali ne nz siyarwa da yake ba wa kowa damar fara kasuwancin yanar gizo ba tare da jari ko kaya ba. Muna yin haka ne ta samar da kayan more rayuwa, kayan siyarwa, da sanin makamar aiki, domin sauƙaƙa wahalar fara shiga kasuwanci a yau. ICAN-BOI Innovation Hub ICAN-BOI wani dandal ine wanda ake samar da lura da cigaban fasaha da samun ƙwarewa ta hanyar bunƙasa sana’ar hannu. Ta ɗauki aniyar zama hanyar haɗa ƙwarewar fasaha da ƙirƙira, wanda ya haɗa har da ɗalibai, harkar ilimi, masu ƙirƙira, masu jari, da masu ilimin cigaban tattalin arziki. Lagos State Employment Trust Fund ( LSETF) Lagos State Employment Trust Fund Law 2016 ne ya samar da Lagos State Employment Trust Fund (LSETF) domin samar da tallafin kuɗi ga mazauna jihar Legas, domin maganin rashin aikin yi ta hanyar samar da aikin yi da kuma kuɗi. Institute of Chartered Accountants of Nigeria(ICAN) Institute of Chatered Accountants of Nigeria ita ce ƙwararriyar cibiya ta akawu a Nijeriya. Ɗaya ce daga cikin ƙwararrun ƙungiyoyi biyu na akawu da suke da damar bayar da dokoki a Nijeriya. Da ilimin fasaharta, dabaru, da kuma ƙwarewa, tana hangen nesa da jagoranci ga ilimin akawu da kuɗi na duniya baki ɗaya. Bank of Industry(BOI) Bank of Industry shi ne development financial institution (DFI) na farko a Nijeriya wanda yake da tsarin canja hukumar masana’antu ta Nijeriya ta hanayar samar da tallafin kuɗi don tabbatar da ƙanana, matsakaita, da manyan masana’antu; tare da faɗaɗawa, bambantawa, da zamanantarwa. Tsarin da ya fuskanci tallafawa ayyuka wanda suke da yiwuwar kawo cigaba. Jobtech Alliance Jobtech Alliance wani tsari ne na gina yanayin muhalli na ayyukan da ake yi a Afirka wanda yake da ra’ayin haɗa mutane ga damarmakin aiki wanda suke gina rayuwa a kyakkyawan mahalli wanda yake bada damar yin sana’a da gina dandali wanda zai dinga isar da saƙo don inganta rayuwa. Salad Afirka Salad yana gina mafita domin canja masu aiki a Afirka ta hanyar tallafawa al’umma da mutanen da suke da kuɗi wanda suke rayuwa mai kyau kuma mafi inganci. Salad Afirka tana haɗin guiwa ne da masu bada aiki don bawa ma’aikatansu wani sashi na kuɗin aikinsu kafin ranar biya saboda a biya buƙatun gaggawa cikin sauƙi wanda shi ne mataki na farko na samun dukiya da ‘yanci.
Sanannen ma’aikacin yaɗa labarai “Do2dtun” ya shiga AltSchool Africa a matsayin Daraktan Gudanarwa na Shiri. ALtSchool Africa, kamfani ne mai tafiyar da koyarwar fasaha wanda ya bada himma a kan mafitar koyon ƙirƙira da damarmakin sana’a, sun yi sanarwar naɗa ma’aikatan yada labarai mafiya shahara, Oladotun Ojuolape Kayode, wanda kuma aka fi sani da Do2dotun, a matsayin Daraktan Gudanarwa na Shiri. A bayanan da aka fitar na kamfanin, Do2dtun zai yi aiki mai matuƙar amfani domin ƙarfafa dangantaka da masu ƙirƙirar shiri, masu koyarwa, da masu fada aji don ƙara Bunƙasa kudurin AItSchool Africa na sauya koyarwa ta yanar gizo a nahiyar baki ɗaya. Tare da aiki mai cike da nasara wanda ya kasance tsawon shekaru ashirin a masana’antar labarai da nishaɗantarwa, Do2dtun ya kawo ƙwarewa da dama, ƙirƙira, da kuma buɗaɗɗiyar hanyar zuwa sabon matsayinsa a ALtSchool Afirka. A matsayinsa na dadadden mai rahoton gidan radiyo, mai gudanar da biki, kuma mai fada aji, Do2dtun ya dade yana nuna ƙaunarsa ga son kawo canji mai kyau ga al’adun matasa da kuma masana’antar nishaɗi baki ɗaya. “Muna farin cikin yin maraba da Do2dtun zuwa cikinmu a matsayin Daraktan Gudanarwa na Shiri,” in ji (Rachel Onoja), Shugaban Aikace-Aikace, ALtSchool Afirka. “Dotun ya yi babban ƙoƙari wajen taimakawa ALtSchool Afirka wajen cika alƙawarinta na sanya koyarwa ta zamo mai daɗi, ƙwarewa, da kuma riba. Ta hanyar rufe gibin da ke tsakanin ALtSchool Afirka da kuma kwararru a harkar masana’anta, a yanzu za mu iya kawo shekarun ilimi mai matuƙar amfani wanda ba a taɓa ba da hangen nesa na ‘yan Afirka da suke son Bunƙasa aikinsu a masana’antun kasuwanci da mishadi.” Muƙamin Do2dtun ya zo ne a lokaci mai matuƙar amfani ga ALtSchool Africa yayin da take cigaba da bunƙasa isarsa da amfani a gurbin edtech. Da irin wannan dabi’ar mai kyau da kuma ƙwarewar da aka samu a fannin ilimin sadarwa, Do2dtun ya shirya don shigewa gaba wajen haɗin guiwa mai ma’ana da aiki tare da masua koyarwa, jarumai, da masu fada aji domin Bunƙasa gabatarwar ALtSchool Afirka sannan a samar da muhallin koyarwa wanda zai yi tafiya sosai ga masu koyo. “ Ina matuƙar farin cikin kasancewa da ALtShool Afirka da kuma bada gudunmawa wajen hanyar ƙirƙirarsu wajen koyarda,” Oladotun Ojuolape ya fada. “ Ilimi wani abu ne mai ƙarfi ga sauyi, kuma na shirya domin bayar da ƙwarewata domin cike gibin da ke tsakanin ƙirƙirar aiki da ƙwarewar koyarwa mai ma’ana. A tare, za mu bawa masu koyo da ke tasowa kwarin guiwa.” Game da ALtSchool Afirka: ALtSchool Afirka wani kamfani ne na basirar fasaha na duniya wanda ya bada himma wajen gyara wajen koyarwa ta hanyar ƙirƙirar fasaha, ƙwarewar koyarwa ta karankai, da kuma hulɗa mai ma’ana. Ta fasahar cutting-edge da kuma aikin da aka shirya shi cikin ƙwarewa, ALtSchool Afirka ta dau aniyar samarwa masu koyo kaya da abubuwan amfani wanda suke buka a cikin wannan duniyar mai sauyawa. Game da Oladotun “Do2dtun” Ojuolape: Oladotun Ojuolape ma’aikacin sadrwa ne a Nijeriya, mai gabatar da bidiyo, mai taka rawa, kuma mai sana’ar yada labarai wanda yake da ƙwarewa ta fiye da shekaru arba’in a masana’antar yada labarai da nishaɗi.
Kamfanin PATRICIA Technologies Limited sun samu babban hannun jari domin bunƙasa ayyuka. Kamfanin Patrichia Technologies Limited sun samu babban hannun jari daga Oluwaseun Dania, babban jami’in Tradefada, ɗaya daga cikin sanannun masu kasuwancin crypto a Nijeriya. Hannun jarin wani manuni ne ga tarin yardar da masu sanya hannun jarin ke da shi a kan hangen nesan Patrichia da kuma mafita ga canjin kasuwanci a Afirka. Sananne a matsayin ɗaya daga manyan kasuwancin crypto a Afirka, Patrichia na amfani da kasancewarsu a kan gaba a cigaban wajen zaman crypto mai tasowa a Afirka ta hanyar haɗin guiwa mai ƙarfi, hulɗa, da hannun jari daga abokan tarayya a duniya baki ɗaya. Oluwaseun Dania sannannen mai sanya hannun jari ne, wanda yake da son tallafawa kasuwancin ƙirƙire-ƙirƙire da ke masana’antu da dama. Yana bada ƙarfin guiwa ga ɗaiɗaikun mutane da masana’antu da su hadu da shi wajen tabbatar da tasowar Patrichia Technologies yayin da kamfanin ke cigaba da wakiltar Afirka a wajen zaman crypto na duniya. A saƙon da aka tura yanar gizo kwanan nan, Mr Oluwaseun ya ce, “Hannun jari na ba wai na kuɗi ba ne kawai; tabbataccen yarda da kai ne ga ƙungiyar da Hanu Fejiro Agbodie yake wakilta wadda take nuna hazaƙa da ƙirƙira a ko da yaushe kuma ta wakilci Nijeriya da Afirka da kyau a faɗin duniya.”. “Tasowar Patrichia zai ƙarfafa masana’antunmu kuma ya ƙara yardar masu amfani da kayanmu. Riba ce gare mu baki ɗaya,” ya ƙarasa faɗi. Da yake tsokaci game da hannun jarin Mr. Dania na note-worthy, Hanu Fejiro, wanda ya samar kuma Babban Shugaba, ya tabbatar da himmarsa don samar da tarihin juriya na kasuwancin yayin da yake nuni ga yawan damarmakin da suke zuwa. “Wannan hannun jarin daga Mr Oluwaseun Dania ya yi alƙawarin ciyar da Patrichia Technologies gaba domin matsar da iyakoki da kuma tabbatar da matsayinsu na masu jagoranci a gurin zaman cypto da ke tasowa a Afirka,” ya bayyana hakan. Da tallafi mara yankewa daga masu hannun jari da kuma abokan kasuwanci, Patrichia na ciyar da wajen zaman crypto na Afirka gaba. Ku tafi da mu a wannan tafiyar yau domin zama ɓangare na wannan jirgin mai tafiya. Patrichia kamfani ne na mafita ga biyan kuɗi da ke kula da ƙarfin fasahar blockchain domin sauƙaƙa amfani da cryptocurrencies a musayar kuɗi da ko da yaushe. Tare da ba da himma mai yawa ga masana’antar crypto, a ko da yaushe muna samar da mafitar ƙirƙira da take kula da buƙatun abokan cinikinmu da abin da suke nema daga gare mu.
Bayan ƙoƙarin samun kuɗin jari daga masu sanya hannun jari, masu farawa na eCommerce ɗin Kenya, Marketforce, yana tara miliyan $1 ga dandalin crowdfunding, Capitalize. Sheƙara ɗaya bayan sanarwar rufe zangonta na A na miliyan $40, MarketForce ta sanar cewa tana samar da miyilan $1 ta WeFunder. “Yayin da muka fara wannan tafiyar, mun bada himmar gina kamfanin Afirka da babu kamarsa wanda yake tallafawa mutanen Afirka, al’umma, da kuma tattalin arziki, kuma wannan al’ummar ita ce hanya ɗaya da za a tabbatar da wannan tsarin. “Muna yin haka ne saboda mun yarda cewa kamfani kamar Marketforce yana bada damar samun tallafin kuɗi, ba ga ‘yankasuwa da kuma abokan hulɗa da mu kewa aiki ba kawai, amma har ga mutanen da suka gane cewa abin da muke ginawa yana da mahimmanci ga nahiyar. Masu farawar suna karɓar hannun jari mai ƙanƙanta kamar $1,000 akan sharuɗɗa daidai da wanda tayi amfani da shi a zagayen zangon A ɗinsu. Duk da haka, an ce ba dukkan masu hannun jari ne za su karɓi kuɗin hannun jarinsu ba. Wanda Tesh Mbaabu da Mesongo Sibuti suka ƙirƙire shi a 2018, MarketForce wajen kasuwanci ne na B2B da yake samar da rarrabawa da aikin kuɗi ga ‘yan kasuwa. Farawa da Kenya, masu farawar tuntuni sun faɗaɗa zuwa ga ƙasashen kusa, wanda ya haɗa da Tanzania, Rwanda, da Uganda. Kuma tana harkoki a Nijeriya. Kamfanin farawa na Y Combinator-backed yana yin aiki ga ‘yan kasuwa fiye da 200,000 a waɗannan ƙasashen biyar kuma sun samu ƙarin kuɗin shiga daga $140,000 a 2021 zuwa miliyan $2.5 a 2022, daidai da jerin Capitalize. Sannan kuma suna so su ƙara faɗaɗa aikinsu zuwa ga wasu ƙasashen guda huɗu. A yayin da MarketForce ta samar da zangonsu na A a 2022, ta yi burin samun yawan ‘yan kasuwa miliyan akan manhajarta ta super maerchant, RejaReja a ƙarshen 2022. Duk da haka, waɗannan shirye-shiryen sun samu matsala bayan wasu daga masu hannun jarin sun kasa cika alƙawarin aika wani ɓangaren jarin da suka yi wa masu farawa. Don maida martani, sun kori ma’aikata 250 suka gyara tsarin kasuwancinsu domin haɓaka riba. A wata tattaunawa da TechCrunch a watan Mayu 2023, Mbaabu, mamallakin Startup, ya bayyana cewa sun rage yawan hanyoyin da ta kama daga 700 zuwa 400 domin ƙara yawan inganci, sun ce kamfanin na kan hanyar samun kuɗin shigarsu wanda ba su taɓa samun irinsa ba.
Wanda ya samar da Kobo360, Obi Ozor, ya shiga majalisar Jahar Enugu a matsayin Kwamishinan Sufuri. Obi Ozor, wanda ya samar da Kobo360, ya samu muƙamin kwamishinan sufuri a jahar Enugu. Ozor wanda ya samar da Kobo360 tare da Ife Oyedele a 2017, an rantsar da shi ne tare da sauran kwamishinoni 19 wanda gwamnan jihar Enugu ne ya rantsar da su, Barr. Peter Mbah, ranar Alhamis, 10 ga Agusta, 2023. A yayin bikin rantsuwar, gwamnan ya bayyana cewa an zaɓi kwamishinonin ne daidai da ƙwarewarsu, bayanan aikinsu na baya, da kuma tarihinsu. Ya kuma bayyana fatansa na cewa mutanen garin za su ga sauyi daga sababbin kwamishinonin da aka naɗa daga kwanaki 100 na farkon shigarsu ofishi. “Muna bayyana babban burinmu wanda zai taimaka mana wajen bunƙasa tattalin arzikinmu da sauri. Kuma mun yi wa mutanenmu alƙawarin yaye talauci da kuma maida Jihar Enugu babban masauƙin saka hannun jari. Waɗannan tunani ne masu amo kuma masu girma. Amma a yayin da muka yi wannan alƙawarin, muna buƙatar ƙungiya da za ta jagoranci mutanenmu daga inda muke a yanzu zuwa wannan wajen da muke son kai su. Saboda wannan dalilin, hanyar da ta samar da zaɓin ka tana da tsauri an kuma bi ta daki-daki. Ozor shi ne mamba na nan kusa daga cikin masu farar da sana'a a Nijeriya da aka ba wa muƙamin siyasa bayan Boson Tijjani da aka sanya shi cikin jerin sunayen wanda za a ba wa muƙamin minister da shugaban ƙasar Nijeriya Bola Ahmed Tinubu ya aika. Babu tabbas idan Ozor zai sauka daga muƙaminsa na Shugaban Kobo360, domin babu wata doka da ta buƙaci masu muƙamin siyasa daga ɓangaren waje da su bar aikinsu na baya.
Dandalin Kasuwancin Jama'a na Yanke-Edge na Vendorstack ya mamaye Nijeriya, yana Sauƙaƙe Siyarwar kan Intanet Kasuwar siye da siyarwa ta dandalin sada zumunta tana ƙara cigaba sosai saboda abokan ciniki suna ƙara yawan siyayya kai tsaye daga dandalin sadar da zumuntar. Kamar yadda bincike na nan kusa ya bayyana, kasuwar siye da siyarwa ta yanar gizo ta duniya an yi aikinta ne domin ta kai biliyan $604.5 a 2027, zuwa ga biliyan $492.2 a 2021. Wannan yana wakiltar CAGR na 3.7% a lokacin da aka yi hasashen. Kasuwancin yanar gizo yana samun ƙarfi a Nijeriya tare da cigaba da yawan amfani da kafar sada zumunta. Nijeriya tana da fiye da miliyan 30 na masu amfani da kafar sada zumunta wanda da yawansu suka fi amfani da Facebook, Instagram, Twitter, da kuma WhatsApp. Wannan ya bada dama mai ƙarfi ta siyayyar dandalin sada zumunta. Kasuwar siye da siyarwa ta Nijeriya an yi ta ne domin kai wa ga samun biliyan $75 zuwa 2025, sama da biliyan $12 a 2018. Kasuwar na samun cigaba ne daga yawan shiga yanar gizo, ma’amala da wayoyin hannu na zamani, da kuma al’ummar matasa masu ta’ammali da fasahar zamani. Kamar yadda wannan rahoton ya bayyana, jimillar Naira miliyan 357 aka rawaito a matsayin damfara ga mutanen da suka siya kaya daga masu siyarwa a Instagram, Naira miliyan 84 ne aka danganta ga musayar kuɗin da ba a amince da shi ba sannan kuma Naira miliyan 273 aka shigar da su a matsayin cikakkiyar damfara daga 2020 – 2021, Da yawa daga mutanen Nijeriya sun samu ɗaya daga cikin wannan damfarar yayin da suke siyayya daga masu siyarwa na dandalin sada zumunta. Vendorstack sun ɗauki aniyar magance babbar matsalar damfara da rashin yarda da yake faruwa a wajen siye da siyarwa na dandalin sada zumunta. Vendorstack, mai samar da mafita ga siye da siyarwar dandalin sada zumunta, ya zamanto amsa ga matsalar damfara ta yanar gizo da rashin yarda ta Nijeriya. An ƙera ta don ta samar da tsarin doka ta bai ɗaya, manhajar tana bada damar sauƙin siye daga farko zuwa ƙarshe da ƙwarewar sayarwa da sayen kayan ta hanyar bada kariya ga dukka mai siyen da mai siyarwar a gaba ɗaya lokacin siyayyar. Manhajar na samar da kulawar kasuwanci ta gaba ɗaya farko zuwa ƙarshe (kula da ƙere-ƙere, jerin kayayyaki, gaban shago, da zaɓin biya mai tsaro) ga masu siyarwar wanda yake cire maimaita hanyar siyarwa ga abokan cinikinsu, yana bayar da tabbacin karɓar kuɗin da aka biya da dama zuwa ga wajen sababbin abokan ciniki. Masu siyayyar a yanar gizo za su iya siya daga masu siyarwar da ƙwarin guiwa a vendorstack ba tare da tsoron damfara ba ko rashin karɓar kuɗinsu ba. Vendorstack a shirye suke don kawo sauyi ga mahallin siye da siyarwa ta yanar gizo a Nijeriya. Ku yi bankwana da matsalolin siye da siyarwa na yanar gizo sannan ku rungumi ƙwarewar cinikayya mara matsala kuma abar yarda. Nijeriya tana da masu amfani da kafafen sada zumunta fiye da miliyan 44, mafi yawa a Afirka. Nijeriya ce take da adaɗi mafi yawa ta mintocin da ake amfani da su a kafafen sada zumunta idan aka haɗa da kowanne ɓangare na duniya. Duka wannan yana nuni ne ga alama mai kyau ta mahallin siye da siyarwa na yanar gizo a Nijeriya, wanda ɗaya ne daga cikin waɗanda Vendorstack take son ta yi aiki a kai. Wanda suka samar da Vendorstack, Ifeoluwa King, da kuma Kazeem Olanipekun sun tabbatarwa da masu kasuwanci cewa za su iya siyar da kaya a yanar gizo ba tare da sun ji tsoron damfara ba da kuma samun kuɗinsu (abin da na siya da abin da na samu). Manhajar da maida hankali ga bada kariya ga masu amfani da ita kuma samar da kayan amfani na yanar gizo ya zanyo musu yarda a mahallin siye da siyarwa na yanar gizo. Tare da mayar da hankali da suke yi a kan bunƙasa aikinsu, Vendorstack ta zamanto abokiyar hulɗa da abar dogaro kuma mai bada goyon baya ga kasuwanci a fagen yanar gizo na yanzu. Vendorstack ta kasance wani aiki mai kawo sauyi a mahallin siye da siyarwa na yanar gizo a Nijeriya, wanda yake magance manyan matsaloli kamar damfara a yanar gizo da rashin yarda. Tare da samarwa da masu kasuwanci wajen tattaunawa a tsakaninsu, samun masu sauraro da dama, da kuma manyan kayan amfani daban-daban, Vendorstack na tallafawa kasuwanci domin su bunƙasa kuma su dama a wannan fage na fasahar zamani. A yayin da muka fara wannan tafiyar ta kawo sauyi a tare, ya kamata Vendorstack ta zamana mai kawo cigaba, ta samar da zamani na yarda da kuma kasuwancin kafar sada zumunci mai nasara a Nijeriya. Ku biyo mu a yau domin buɗe kasuwancinku a yanar gizo mai cikakken amfani tare da Vendorstack! Domin ƙarin bayani, ku bibiyi Vendorstack a kan dukkan shafukansu na dandalin sada zumunta;
Ana gabatar da Roqqu: Hanyarku ta shiga Crypto a Ghana Muna farin cikin sanar muku da ƙaddamar da Roqqu, manhajar kawo sauyi wadda za ta kawo duniyar cryptocurrency ga al’aummar Ghana. Roqqu ya zarce musayar cryptocurrency kawai; mafitarka ce ta bai ɗaya don saurin siya, siyarwa da kuma kula da kadarorin fasahar zamani. Tallafawa masu Ƙaunar Crypto a ƙasar Ghana Tare da yawaitar ra’ayin duniya a kan cryptocurrency, Roqqu ta yarda da buƙatar manhaja da za a dogara da ita kuma wanda masu amfani za su ji daɗinta da ta dace da mutanen Ghana. Burinmu shi ne mu tallafawa mutanen Ghana domin su dama a cikin ƙayatacciyar duniyar cryptocurrencies yayin da suke samar da manhajar musayar kuɗi mai tsaro kuma mai inganci. Game da Roqqu: Roqqu manhaja ce mai jagorancin cryptocurrency wadda take samarwa da masu amfani da ita hanya mara gargada mai tsaro domin siye, siyarwa, da kuma kula da cryptocurrencies. Tare da manufar tafiyar da amfani da cryptocurrency a kasuwanni masu tasowa, Roqqu na bayar da fagen tattaunawa a tsakanin juna wanda zai yi wa masu amfani daɗi, cryptocurrencies daban-daban, alamomi na tsaro masu ƙarfi. Ka sauke manhajar Roqqu a nan Apple Store da kuma Google Play Store. Me ya sa za a zaɓi Roqqu? Ƙwarewa Sauƙaƙƙa: An tsara Roqqu ne tare da la'akari da bukatun ka. Tattaunawar tunaninmu a tsakanin juna yana sauƙaƙawa masu farawa da wanda suke da ƙwarewa wajen shiga duniyar cryptocurrencies. Cryptocurrencies masu yawa: Ka duba rabe-raben cryptocurrencies, daga Bitcoin zuwa Etherium har fiye da haka. Roqqu ya bayar da zaɓi daban-daban domin dacewa da zaɓinka na zuba jari. Musayar kuɗi mai tsaro: Tsaronku shi ne abin da muka ba wa himma. Roqqu sun samar da matakai na tsaro da encryption na zamani domin bada kariya ga musayar kuɗinka da kuma bayanai da suka shafe ka. Ajiyar kuɗi da cirewa na nan take: Ka yi bankwana da lokacin jira. Tare da Roqqu, za ka ji daɗin ajiyar kuɗi da cirewa nan take, yana ba ka sassauyawar da ka cancanta. Tallafar abokin ciniki na 24/7: Kana da tambayoyi ne ko kana buƙatar taimako? Ƙungiyarmu mai himma da ke bada tallafi ga abokan ciniki tana nan a kowanne lokaci domin kula da damuwarku da kuma ba ku haske. Yadda za ka Fara Farawa da Roqqu abu ne mai sauƙi. Ka buɗe akawun a manhajarmu mai sauƙin amfani, ka cika tsarin tantancewa, kuma ka shirya don fara kasuwancin cryptocurrencies. Ko da ka kasance ɗan kasuwa mai ƙwarewa ne ko kuma a yanzu ka fara tafiyar crypto, Roqqu na samar da dukkan kayan aikin da kake buƙata don samun nasara. Hangen nesan Roqqu game da Ghana A Roqqu, mun yarda da sauyi mai amfani na cryptocurrencies domin kawo sauyin zamani ga hanyoyin kuɗi da kuma tallafawa mutane. Tare da ƙaddamarwarmu a Ghana, mun bada himma wajen tabbatar da tafiya da cryptocurrecies a yankin. Ku biyo mu a wannan tafiyar mai ƙayatarwa yayin da muke share hanya ta gaba inda tallafin kuɗi zai samu. Ku ziyarci www.roqqu.com domin ƙarin bayani da kuma farawa a yau. Roqqu: Tallafawa Ghana; Ka yi abubuwa da yawa da crypto…. Ka duba don ganin wasu abubuwan a nan
Labari mai ƙayatarwa ga Al’ummar Samar da Kayayyaki a Afirka: Ka ba wa abokan hulɗa na Afirka ƙarfin guiwa da ProductDive! Muna matuƙar farin cikin sanar da labari mai ƙayatarwa wanda zai bunƙasa ƙwarewarka ta koyo da shiga yanar gizo. Hulɗa tsakanin manyan taruka biyu sun shirya domin sake tsara mahalli na damarmakin tafiyar da kayayyaki. Muna farin cikin sanar da Taron haɗin guiwar fasaha tsakanin ProductDive da kuma Inspire Afirka, wanda Silicon Valley Product Group suka shirya. Haɗa waɗannan dandali masu ƙarfi guda biyu yana nufin dukkan masu halarta da suke da tikitin The Dive a yanzu ana gayyatarsu da su shiga Taron Inspire AFRICA- a KYAUTA! Eh, daidai ka ji. Duk a cikin wannan haɗin guiwar na fasaha, muna buɗe kofa ne ga duniyar fahimta, haɗi, da kuma cigaba. Da duka Taron The Dive da kuma Inspire Africa da suka haɗu waje ɗaya, ba sai ka yi zaɓi tsakanin manyan taruka biyu ba. Duka suna kusa da kai! Wannan haɗin guiwa shi muka ba wa himma domin ƙarfafar al’umma masu samar da kayayyaki da take tasowa a Nijeriya da sama da haka. Ya ƙunshi cire da ke tsakani, faɗaɗa hangen nesa, da samar da cikakkiyar ƙwarewa da take tallafa maka wajen isa babban mataki a matsayin shugabannin kayayyaki. Kuma domin a yi murna, ProductDive tana bayar da ragin 15% daga kuɗin tikitinsu na taron da za a yi ranar Asabar, Agusta 12th. Ku danna mahaɗar domin siyan tikitin. Ku yi amfani da lambar garaɓasar ta DIVESVPG15 Ku sanya alama ajikin kalandarku, ku shirya domin shiga cikin kula da kayayyaki ta nan gaba, ku rungumi wannan damar ta musamman domin ba wa Afirka Ƙarfin guiwa da ƙwarewar kayayyakinku.
OAU, CU su ne suke samar da lamba mafi yawa ta ‘millionaire’ wanda suka samar da West Africa startup a shekarun da suka gabata. Ranar Litinin, 5 ga Oktoba, 2020, Techpoint Africa ta ƙaddamar da rahotonta na tsahon shekaru na West Africa Startup. Rahoton ya maida hankali ne a kan ayyukan tallafi na kuɗi ga masu farawa a mahallin fasaha daga 2010 da 2019. Ya ƙunshi bayanai na ayyukan tallafi daga masana’antun masu farawa, asalin masu sanya hannun jari, da sanannun masana’antu, da sauran su. Abin lura ne cewar Millionaire West Africa Startup (MWAS) – su ne kawai Kamfani mai Farawa a Afirka ta Yamma da ta samar da miliyan $1 a haɗe- a cikin lokacin da ake magana aka, aka saka a cikin rahoton. Mayar da hankali gaba ɗaya a kan ilimin masu samar da masu sun bayyana cewa Jami’ar Obafemi Awolowo (OAU) da Jami’ar Covenant (CU) sun samar da tsofaffin ɗalibai 12, ɗaya na bin ɗaya, domin zama a bigire na farko da na biyu a sakamakon maƙarantar da digiri na farko. Abin sha’awa, wani yayi da ya yawaita cewa wanda suka samar da MWAS daga jami’a ɗaya sun samar da kamfanoni a tare. Kuɗi, alal misali, yana da wanda suka samar da MWAS daga Jami’ar Obafemi Awolowo; sauran kamfanoni masu farawa da wanda suka samar da su daga OAU su ne TeamApt, Terragon, Farmcrowdy, 54gene, SlimTrader, da kuma PropertyPro. Jami’ar Covenant ma tana da masu samarwa wanda Startup ɗinsu su ne—PiggyVest, MDAAS, da Kora Network—sun fito a cikin rahoton. Zai nuna cewa waɗannan maƙarantun ko dai suna da ƙarfin samar da ɗalibai waɗanda suke zuwa suna samar da Startup mai cike da nasara ko kuma waɗannan daliban suna neman hanya ne, bayan gama maƙaranta, wadda take ba su damar haɗuwa a tare domin fara waɗannan kamfanonin. Koma menene dalilin, waɗannan maƙarantun su ke samar da mafi yawan masu ƙirƙirar MWAS a shekarun baya masu yawa. Domin samun ƙarin bayani, ka nemi rahoton West African Startup Decade. Nick Fewings ne ya samar da hoton da aka nuna a kan Unsplash
Opay na Nijeriya ya zamo na gaba a mahallin Fintech, wanda ya samu shaidar matsayi na CNBC da Statista na duniya a matsayin manhajar zamani kaɗai ta Nijeriya a ɓangaren biyan kuɗi na zamani . A wata babbar nasara, Opay ya ɗaga zuwa ga jerin farko na tsarin fintech a Nijeriya, wanda ya samu babban matsayi na cikakkiyar manhajar biyan kuɗi a jerin matsayi na CNBC da Statista. Daga dukkan faɗin duniya, wanda ya hada da manhajar hada-hadar kuɗi daban-daban, CNBC; hanyar sadarwa ta talabijin ta duniya wadda take aiki awa 24 kai tsaye, kasuwar duniya ta bayanan kuɗi da shirye-shirye, da kuma sanannen kamfanin bincike game da kasuwa mai zaman kansa Statista sun yi haɗin guiwa domin su samar da jerin sunaye mai faɗi da zai haskaka kamfanoni taron mutane masu fasahar ƙirƙira, kayayyakin kuɗi da suka cika da fasaha da kuma ayyuka. Himmar haɗin guiwarsu ya haifar da tattara manyan kamfanonin fintech guda 200, tare da aiki da tsararraun hanyoyi domin duba ƙoƙarin kamfanonin a cikin masu nuna da suke da matuƙar mahimmanci wanda ya shafi ƙarfin mai amfani, ƙarfin musayar kuɗi, da kuma kuɗin shiga. Kamfanonin da aka gabatar an raba su ne cikin ƙwarewa zuwa gida tara: bankunan zamani, biya ta yanar gizo, kadara ta yanar gizo, tsarin kuɗi na yanar gizo, da kuma kula da dukiya ta yanar gizo, tallafin kuɗi da ake da shi, bayar da bashi da ake da shi, mafita ga bankuna ta yanar gizo, da kuma mafita ga kasuwanci ta yanar gizo. Jerin sunayen ya bayyana kamar su Paypal, Revolut, WISE, da kuma wasu daga cikin manyan masu damawa a mahallin fintech a duniya. Opay ya samu shiga a ɓangaren biyan kuɗi a yanar gizo daga wannan jerin sunayen mai matsayi. Yawan buƙata ga mafitar biyan kuɗi ta yanar gizo mara tangarɗa a cikin Nijeriya ya haskaka hanyar Opay, wanda ya sanya ya zamanto mai saurin gaske, mai tsaro, kuma manhajar da za a dogara da ita wajen kowanne irin musayar kuɗi. Wannan sanin na duniya shi ya ƙara tabbatar da himmarmu wajen sauya mahallin biyan kuɗi na yanar gizo a Nijeriya da wajen ta,”Adekunle Adeyemi ya yi bayani, Shugaban Ɓangaren Tallatawa na Opay. “Yana bayyana abin da muka tsara za mu yi a matsayin kamfani, da kuma abin da mutanenmu suke himmatuwa domin cim ma burin. Muna matuƙar alfaharin kasancewa masu haskakawa ga ƙirƙira da kuma nutsuwa a cikin masana’antar fintech ta Nijeriya, kuma wannan cigaban ne yake ƙara mana ƙaimin himmarmu, da kuma kasancewarmu ga fuskantar abokn kasuwancinmu da ba sa yankewa,” ya ƙara da hakan. A cikin wannan lokacin na babbar matsala a mahallin fintech, ƙarancin tallafi, da kuma zuwa ga matakan yanke farashi, Opay sun yi ƙoƙari wajen samar da kayayyaki na musamman da ayyuka domin taimakawa da tallafawa abokan ciniki yayin da suke samar da yanayin musamman ga abokan ciniki.
Yadda Bankly yake sake tsarin ajiya ga Jama'a na yau da Kullum Ka san yadda suke cewa kishiyar hakan na janyo hankali? To, wannan ne daidai yadda za ka kwatanta abotar da ke tsakanina da Susan, ‘daɗaɗɗiyar aminiyta da muke komai tare’. Ni da Susan muna da bambanci a ɗabi’a, kuma wannan yanayin ya kasance a haka a gaba ɗaya shekaru ashirin na kawancen mu. A yayin da nake ƙoƙarin riƙo da ɗadi’u masu cike da raha, Susan ta kasance mai nutsuwa, mai taka tsantsan. Tana da duba abu da dogon nazari da kuma tunanin iya tsari. Duk da bambancin dabi’unmu, da ni da Susan muna da tunani iri ɗaya wajen adana kuɗi. Muna yawan tattauna hanyoyi mabambanta domin kula da harkokin kuɗinmu, matsalarmu ta nan kusa ita ce tanadi mai amfani wajen tara kuɗi domin gabatowar murnar ranar haihuwar mahaifiyarta na shekaru 50. Iyalin sun yanke shawarar tarar wannan cigaban mai mahimmanci da biki na musamman. Saboda haka, duk yadda ‘yan’uwanta suke son bada gudunmawarsu domin bikin, ita ke da nauyin kulawa da waɗannan gudunmuwar yadda ya kamata. Ta yi tunanin sake komawa ga”Ajo”, wata daɗaɗɗiyar hanyar adana kuɗi ta al’umma. Wannan hanyar tara kuɗin ta nuna alamun hanya ce ta nutsuwa ta tara kuɗin don yin bikin. Saboda haka, ta sani daga ƙwarewa cewa hanyar na da nata matsalolin, kuma damfara ta zama ruwan dare. Gabatar da ‘yan’uwanta ga kungiyar “ Ajo” abu ne mai haɗari. Idan wani ya gudu da kuɗinsu, zai iya janyo rigima tsakaninta da ‘yan’uwanta. Ya kamata ta nemo wata hanyar. Neman mafita ga Susan ya kai ta ga Bankly Microfinance Bank. Suna bayar da damar tara kuɗi a ƙungiyance a manhajar ta Bankly wanda ya zamanantar da hanyar al’adar ta “Ajo”. Ya zamanto kamar gada ce da ta haɗa son tara kuɗi na al’ada tare da nutsuwar kayan aiki na zamani. Da wannan yanayin, Susan za ta iya samun ƙwarin guiwar jan ra’ayin ‘yan’uwanta game da tara kudi don bikin mai gabatowa. Yanayin ajiyar kuɗi a Ƙungiyance Bankly na wani mataki ne na ƙirƙira domin ajiyar kuɗi na al’umma wanda yake samar da gaskiya da amana. Yana haɗa yanayin samuwa, da kuma mu'amala mai kyau ga masu amfani, da kuma mayar da hankali game da amana domin ba wa mutane kamar Susan dama a lokacin da suke son ajiyar kuɗi domin buƙatu masu mahimmanci. Yanayin Ajiyar Kuɗin a Ƙungiyance haka nan yana bada kuɗin ruwa na shekara a kashi 15% na abin da aka samu a rana, domin samar da dama don cigaba mai ɗorewa zuwa wani lokaci. Wannan ba shi ke nan ba. Masu amfani za su iya saita tsarin ajiyar kuɗi, da yawan kuɗin, da kuma lokacin da ya isa a ɗiba domin tsarin tara kuɗi na ƙungiyarsu, domin nuna yanayin haɗin kai wajen lamuran kuɗi da kuma rarraba ayyuka. Domin samar da amana sosai, yanayin ajiyar kuɗin ƙungiyar an tsara shi ne domin samarwa da ‘yan ƙungiyar alama ta nan take na kuɗin da aka saka da kuma wanda aka cire, domin tabbatar da cewa kowa ya samu bayani, wanda hakan zai taimaka wajen sanya nutsuwa ga masu sanya kuɗinsu da kuma samar da yarda a tsakanin juna a ƙungiyar. Daidai da manufarsu, Bankly Microfinance Bank ya dage wajen sake saita mahallin kuɗin da kuma tallafawa mutane ɗaiɗaiku kamar Susan ta hanyar yanayin kayayyakin da suke kula da dukkan ƙalubale na yau da kullum. Suna canja tsarin ajiyar kuɗin daga aiki, zuwa ga ɓangaren rayuwa da yake taimakawa mutane su cim ma cigaban kansu , na iyali, da kuma kasuwanci. Domin ƙarin bayani game da Yanayin Bankly na Ajiye Kuɗi a Ƙungiyance, ka danna nan domin kallon bidiyon demo, ko ka ziyarci shafin bankly.ng.
Kwalejin Senior Model Badore ta Jihar Legas ta ci Gasar Babban Project iCommunity STEAM wadda aka shirya domin maƙarantun gwamnati a Jihar Legas Chevron Nigeria Limited (CNL) tare da haɗin guiwar Nigerian National Petroleum Limited (NNPC) tare da STEAM Fun Fest suka shirya gasar Project iCommunity STEAM. Ɗalibai 500 daga maƙarantun gwamnati da ke ƙarƙashin State Education District III na Jihar Legas ne suka fafata a gasar mai amfani ta STEAM wadda ta himmatu wajen samar da zurfafan tunani da kuma dabarun magance matsala a tsakanin ɗalibai matasa. Project iCommunity da STEAM Fun Fest ta shirya tare da haɗin guiwar Education District III ta jihar Legas, STEAM UP Lagos ta fara ne da bayar da horo ga malamai guda 20 da kuma makonni 4 na bayar da horon tunanin zane-zane ga ɗalibai 10 a gaba ɗaya gundumar. Matakin ƙarshe na gasar ya kasance ne ranar Asabar, 8 ga Yuli, 2023, wanda a sannan maƙarantun da aka zaɓa suka gabatar da aikinsu na farko ga manyan alƙalai, masana ilimi, da kuma ƙungiyoyi masu bada tallafi. Babbar Kwalejin Model ta Jihar Legas, Badore ta cinye gasar ta STEAM dalilin aikinsu na gorar ruwan zafi mai amfani da baturin hasken rana, inda suka samu kyautar Naira 1,000,000. Babbar Maƙarantar Kwalejin Kuramo da ke Victoria Island sun zamanto a mataki na biyu dalilin aikinsu na kyamarar CCTV marar waya mai ƙayatarwa, inda suka samu kyautar Naira 500,000. Babbar Maƙaranta ta King Ado ce ta zo a mataki na uku inda suka samu kyautar Naira 250,000 dalilin aikinsu na Wooden Walking Way, yayin da Babbar Maƙarantar Mata ta Academy Lagos Island, tare da aikinsu na Manhajar KoyonI, da kuma Babbar Kwalejin Gwamnati Ikoyi da aikinsu na Ƙwan Lantarki mai Amfani da Hasken Rana duka suka ci Naira 100,000, a mataki na 4 da na 5 jere. Dukkan ayyukan guda 10 sun yi nuni da haɗin kai da kuma mayar da hankali wajen magance matsalolin zurfin tunani. Kamar yadda Jadesola Adedji ya bayyana ɗaya daga cikin masu shiryawa na STEAM Fun Fest, “muna matuƙar alfahari da ƙyayataccen cigaban da dukkan ‘yan takara suka gabatar. A wannan gasar ta STEAM ta wannan shekarar, babban abin da muka ba wa mahimmanci shi ne na sanya ra’ayin koyo, magance matsala, da kuma ƙirƙira a tsakanin matasa na jihar Legas. Ƙwarin guiwar da muka samu daga ɗaliban farin ciki ya sanya mana ƙwarin guiwar domin cigaba da nema, tare da burin faɗaɗa wannan ƙirƙirar ga maƙarantu da ba a cikin Legas kawai ba hatta gaba ɗaya Nijeriya.” Ta godewa Chevron Nigeria Limited, Nigerian National Petroleum Limited (NNPCL), dangane da goyon bayansu da kuma tallafi, wanda ya tabbatar da nasarar gasar ta STEAM. “Himmatuwarsu wajen bunƙasa fasahar matasan ɗalibai da kuma kuma ciyar da ilimi gaba a jihar Legas abu ne da aka jinjina masa,” ta ƙara da haka. STEAM Fun Fest na da haɗin guiwar kamfanoni masu jagoranci guda 4 na Edtech-9ijakids, STEM-METS, Edufun Technik, da kuma Sabiteach.
Tallafawa SMEs a Kwara: Trade Lenda SME Fair sun yi haɗin guiwa da gwamnatin Jihar Kwara da kuma DTO Foundation domin tasiri mai daɗewa. Trade Lenda SME Fair tana afaharin sanar da cewa ta haɗa guiwa da gwamnatin jihar Kwara da kuma Dr. Toba Oloyede (DTO) Foundation domin taimakawa cigaba da kuma tafiyar da ƙanana da kuma matsakaitan sana’o’i (SME) a cikin jihar ta hanyar tallafawa masu sana’ar hannu guda 7, wanda za su dama a cikin sanannen bikin Trade Lenda SME Fair a jihar Lagos. Wanda zai kasance a Agusta 19, Trade Lenda SME Fair shi ne taro mafi girma na SME a Nigeria, shugabannin masana’antu, da kuma jami’an gwamnati. Wannan tallafin yana nuna himmar jihar Kwara da kuma DTO Foundations wajen tallafawa kasuwancin cikin gida da kuma kula da cigaban tattalin arziki a yankin. Dukkan ɓangarorin sun gane mahimmiyar rawar da SME suke takawa wajen tafiyar da cigaban tattalin arziki da kuma samar da damarmakin aikin yi. Ta hanyar tallafawa waɗannan masu sana’ar hannu na musamman guda 7 don su dama a cikin Trade Lenda SME Fair, Jihar Kwara da DTO Foundation sun maida hankali wajen samar musu da manhaja domin bayyana kayan da suka samar da ayyukansu. Trade Lenda SME Fair suna bayar da dama ta musamman ga masu sana’ar hannu domin haɗuwa da ƙwararru game da masana’antu, abokan hulɗa na ƙwarai, da kuma ‘yan mabanbanta na abokan ciniki na nan gaba. Ta hanyar damawa a Trade Lenda SME Fair, masu sana’o’in hannu da aka ɗauki nauyinsu za su samu bayanai masu amfani, za su haɗa alaƙa mai amfani da kasuwanci, kuma su faɗaɗa kasuwancinsu. Masu halarta za su sa ran ganin SME mabanbanta tare da kayan da suke ƙirƙira, tare da ragi na musamman a kan waɗannan kayayyakin. Yin rijista domin Trade Lenda Fair 2023 na cigaba har a yanzu, kuma muna shawartar mutane da su mallaki tikitinsu a yanzu. Ku samu tikitinku a nan: http://tix.africa/discover/tradelenda Game da Trade Lenda Trade Lenda banki ne na yanar gido wanda yake a kan gaba da aka yi shi domin tallafawa matsakaita da ƙananan masana’atu (SMEs) a Nijeriya. Ta hanyar babban tsarin na ayyukan kuɗi, wanda suka haɗa da bashi, ajiya da kuma inshora, Trade Lenda yana son cim ma bunƙasa tattalin arziki, ‘yancin samun kuɗi da kuma ƙoƙarin samar da yanayin mahalli da take tallafawa nasarar SMSs.
Gina Gaba: Maƙarantar Kasuwanci ta Legas za ta gabatar da taron Tech Founders na farko. Babbar Maƙarantar Kasuwanci ta Legas (LBS) za ta yi taron masu faɗa a ji na Nigerian tech ecosystem a karon farko na tech Founders Summit a cikin ɗakin taron maƙarantarsu da ke Ajah, Legas, a ranar talata, 17 Agusta, 2023. Taron wanda yake da taken “Building the Future:Technology, Innovation, and Entrepneurship” wanda yake son tattaro kan masu ƙirƙirar fasaha, masu hannun jari, shugabannin masana’antu da kuma ƙwararru, mahukunta, malamai, da masu sha’awar fasaha waje ɗaya domin tattauna cigaban mahallin fasaha ta Nijeriya. Yayin magana da Techpoint Africa game da dalilin da ya sa LBS ta haɗa taron, Segun Thomas, Shugaban Samar da Kaya da kuma ƙirƙira a LBS, ya ce, “Mun ga mutane da yawa suna shiga mahallin fasaha na kamfani mai tasowa, amma maƙasudin har yanzu babu shi. Wasu masu samarwar masu fasaha ne, amma fahimtar abin da ya haɗa kula da kasuwanci da kuma fasaha har yanzu yana da wahala ga wasu. Burin LBS ga wannan taron shi ne su ba mu damar zuwa da wasu maganin matsala wanda yake tare da buƙatun waɗannan kamfanoni masu farawa ɗin saboda suna da ƙalubale da dama. Don LBS ta zo da wasu kayayyaki da kuma maganin matsala a wannan fagen, da farko sai mun fara fahimtar matsalar da suke fuskanta, kuma muna da buƙatar haɗa dukkan masu gudanarwa a cikin tsarin.” Ya ƙara da cewa suna ƙoƙarin samun mahalli inda ake ganin buƙatar masu sanya hannun jari, masu samarwa, da kuma mutane da suke ƙoƙarin kawo gyara a mahallin, kuma suna da damar samar da wani abu a kan matsalar wanda yake magance abin da ya damu masu gudanarwar a mahallin fasahar. Abin da ya kamata ka yi zato game da taron Tech Founders Damarmakin haɗuwa da manyan mutane:Taron zai samar da manhaja ga masu zuwa taron domin haɗuwa da mahukunta da kuma masu samarwa. Samar musu damar manyan damarmaki na ƙulla kasuwanci. Hange daga shugabannin masana’antu: Masu shiga taron kuma su saurari ji daga masu hannun jari, masu samarwa, mahukunta, da sauran shugabannin masana’antu daga sauransu. Za su saurari tattaunawa a kan yadda zasu binciki matakai da dama na cigaba, daga neman jari zuwa ga sanin abin da masu hannun jari suke da buƙata, kula da buriƙa, sannan mafi amfani, yadda zasu bunƙasa a masana’antunsu. Gudunmawa game da tattaunawar: Masu shiga tsarin za su samu damar tattaunawa da kuma taimakawa wajen cigaban tsarin mahallin fasahar Nijeriya. Cikakkun hanyoyin magance matsaloli daga LBS: Masu tsarawar, Makarantar Kasuwanci ta Legas, ta tsara bunƙasa magance matsala ta masu gudanarwa bisa ga hangen nesa da kuma tattaunawa yayin taron. Waɗanda ake tunanin za su yi bayani a taron su ne waɗannan shugabannin masana’antun: Olugbenga Agboola, Shugaba kuma wanda ya samar da Flutterwave; Dr Ola Brown, Shugaba kuma wadda ta samar da HealthCap Afirka; Dr Bosun Tijani, Shugaba kuma wanda ya samar da CcHub; Oswald Guabadia, tsohon Babban Mataimakin Shugaban Ƙasa a kan harkar fasahar zamani;Goke Olubisi, Shugaba kuma wanda ya samar da Helium Health; Professor Olayinka David West, Associate Dean, Maƙarantar Kasuwanci ta Legas, daga cikin manyan mutane sanannu. Domin halartar taron Tech Founders, masu sha’awar za su iya yin rijista ta amfani da mahaɗi da aka samar:http:?//bit.ly/tech-founders-summit. Da akwai damarmakin tallafi da kuma baje haja domin masu kasuwancin da suke da ra’ayin nuna magancewar matsala a taron. Wasu daga cikin abubuwan da aka buɗewa masu kasuwanci sun haɗa da wayewa, Ƙarin damarmakin hanyoyi, da kuma samun abokan ciniki, daga cikinsu.
Bankin Raven ya tallafawa ɗalibai 400,000 da sabuwar fasahar ‘Intanet mai Fukafuki’- WiFi na Kyauta a Harabar maƙarantar Ta dalilin Feather Interpret Initiative, Bankin Raven sun fara tallafawa ɓangaren ilimi ta hanyar samar da wifina kyauta a harabar maƙarantun Nijeriya. Kyautar BAFI,2022 Neo Bank ta shekara, ta bayyana tunanin ranar Juma’a yayin ƙaddamar da Raven Feather Internet a Jami’ar Ignatius Ajuru, Rumolumeli, Pot Harcourt, a jihar Rivers. Yayin murnar cigaban, Uchennan Nnodim, Babban Daraktan Bankin Raven, ya bayyana cewa wannan ne mataki na farko na manufar bankin don tallafawa ɗalibai fiye da 400,000 a faɗin jami’oin Tarayya da na jaha da ke ƙasar da yanar gizo mai ƙarfi da sauri domin taimakawa ƙwazon ƙaratu. Ya bayyana cewa tunanin ya zamanto wata dabara don kawo gyara ga rarrabuwar fasaha da ke zuwa daga ƙarancin damar samun yanar gizo, matsalar da ɗaliban Nijeriya da dama suka fuskanta. Bayar da misali daga yadda ya samu nasa ilimin, ya bayyana matsalolin da ya fuskanta wajen samun bayanai a yanar gizo. Wannan, tare da yanda Raven ya mayar da hankali wajen samun ilimin kuɗi tsakanin Gen Z da millennials, shi ne ya haifar da wannan hangen nesan mai amfani. Ya ce, “mun fahinmci cewa kusan kaso 70 na ɗaliban Nijeriya ba su da damar shiga yanar gizo. Wannan adaɗi ne mai girma. Sannan kuma muna da cikakken sani cewa a lokutan zamani yawan bayanai da ilimin da yake a yanar gizo ba abin da za a wuce gona da iri ba ne.” “Za ka iya samun damar kowanne irin ilimi ko bayanai da yanar gizo, don haka samun damar shiga yanar gizo abu ne mai matuƙar amfani ga cigaban ilimi da kuma ƙaratu.” Nnodim ya cigaba da cewa ƙaddamarwar farko a IAUE ita ce matakin farko na cigaban. “Ƙaddamarwarmu ta yau (Juma’a) ita ce wajen mu na farko, amma muna da babban shiri domin aikin. Na riga na faɗa cewar muna so mu isa ga aƙalla ɗalibai 400,000, kuma ma har mun samo wasu wuraren guda 26 da muke so mu faɗaɗa.” “Muna kan tattaunawa da hukumomi sauran waɗannan wuraren, kuma tattaunawar tana tafiya ba wata matsala. Shirinmu shi ne mu aiwatar a waɗannan wurare a kwata ta biyu ta 2024,”ya faɗa. Ƙaddamar da Raven Feather Internet na gaske ya fara ne da tattaunawa ta tsawon awa ɗaya, wanda Shugaban Raven Chidinma Maduwesi ya gabatar, wanda ya fito da sanya tattaunawa a kan darussa da suka shafi ajiya, sanya hannun jari, sana’ar hannu, da sauransu. Shugabannin tattauawar sun haɗa da Uchenna Nnodim, Shugaban Raven, Raven POS aggregator Benjamin Idris, da kuma Kelechi Godfrey, mai koyar da harkokin kuɗi daga The Bedroom. Kuma ɗalibai sun nishaɗantu a rabin lokacin taron da abubuwan nishaɗi daga zaɓaɓɓun fasihai. Kuma cikin wanda suka halarci ƙaddamarwar akwai Professor Okey Okechukwu, Shugaban Jami’ar Ilimi ta Ignatius Ajuru. A bayaninsa, ya yaba wa masu gudunarwar Raven game da nasarar aikinsu wajen aiwatarwa da gabatar da Ƙaddamarwar Intanet mai Fukafuki a harabar jami’oi. A lokaci guda, ya kuma ya ba wa bankin wajen zabar maƙarantar domin gabatar da aikin. Ya kuma ƙarfafawa ɗaliban guiwa da su yi amfani da yanar gizo ta kyauta a harabar jami’ar, ya ƙara da cewa ita yanar gizon ba ƙarfafa ƙaratu kawai take ba sai dai tana ƙara buɗe idon ɗaliban zuwa ga dabaru da dama, da tallafa musu a gaba ɗayan rayuwar ƙaratunsu da kuma fiye da haka. Don tabbatar da amfanin Intanet mai Fukafuki, Nnodim ya bayyana, “wannan shirin an tsara shi ne kawai don ya samar da amfani mai yawa a rayuwar ɗaliban Nijeriya.” An yi shi ne da manufar ba wa ɗalibai 400,000 damar amfani da yanar gizo ta kyauta a kowacce rana; wannan shi ne ƙaddamarwar farko kuma a waje ɗaya kawai, muna da niyyar kai wa wasu jami’o’in. Manufar ita ce a tabbatar da cewa ɗalibai sun samu damar shiga yanar gizo domin neman iliminsu, domin bincike sannan kuma ya ba su damar samun kowanne irin ilimi suke da ra’ayi.” Yayin bayani game da tunanin da ke da alaƙa da sunan, ya nuna cewa fukafukan hankaka mai girman gaske, sa’ar kamfanin, shi ya haifar da sunan. Koyi da saurin fukafukansa, ƙungiyar suka sanyawa hanyar sadarwar ƙetare iyakoki, don sauya hadahadar fasahar zamani tayi sauri la'akari da fukafukansa. Domin samun ƙarin bayani game da Shirin Fukafuki na Intanet mai ilmantarwa da kuma zama wani ɓangare na wannan tafiya mai tarihi, ka bibiyi Raven Bank@theravenbank a dukkan manhajoji. Game da Bankin Rven: Bankin Raven ”Raven” ko “RMFB” banki ne na zamani da yake samar da ayyukan hada-hadar kuɗi cikin sauri, aminci da kuma dogaro ga mutanen Afirka farawa daga Nijeriya. “People’s of bank ofa Afirka” – Bankin Raven ya kasance a sahun farko na ƙirƙira, wanda ya dage wajen tabbatar da haɗuwa da kuma ilimantuwa ta hanayar hangensu na Feather Internet Program. Tare da cikakken mayar da hankali wajen tallafawa ɗalibai da kuma daidaita rabuwar fasahar zamani, Raven Bank yana hango wata duniya da fasaha ke azurta rayuka da kuma tabbatar da mafarkai. Sauke manhajar Bankin Raven.
