saha. A NewDev.io, zaku samu kayan karatu na zamani, da kuma ɗan jagora na ƙashin kai daga ƙwararru a harkokin fasaha. Dangane da Haɗin Gwiwar: Wannan haɗin gwiwar zai taimaka wajen bada kyakkyawan sakamako ga ɓangarorin biyu. Yunƙurin HM Community na bada ƙarfi wajen yin jagora da kuma tallafawa al'umma; yazo daidai da ƙudurin NewDev.io na ganin sun wadata al'umma da ilimin fasaha. A tare da juna, su biyun zasu samar da wani ƙwaƙƙwaran yanayi da zai tallafawa mutane, da kuma share musu hanya su fito da baiwawwakinsu don samun cimma nasara a duniyar fasaha. Abinda zasu gabatar: A matsayin wani ɓangare na wannan haɗakar, muna masu farin cikin gabatar da wata kyakkyawar dama, -wani shirin bada horo kyauta na tsawon wata biyu.! Ko sabon shiga ne kai a harkar fasaha, ko wanda zai canza sana'a zuwa harkar fasaha, ko wanda ke neman sabbin damammaki don cigaba, wannan horon an tsara shi yanda zai dace da buƙatun ka. A tsawon lokacin bada wannan horaswa na wata biyu, zaku natsa izuwa cikin ƙayatacciyar duniyar tsare-tsare, naƙaltar muhimman dabaru da kuma ilimai da zasu ɗora ku a gwadaben kaiwa ga nasara. Ta hanyar gudanar da bincike na ƙashin kanku, fuskantar ƙalubalen duniya, da kuma shawarwari daga ƙwararru a harkokin fasaha, zaku samu ƙwarara gwiwar da kuke buƙata don yin zarra a harkar fasaha. Ba kuma shikenan ba! Bayan kammala karɓar horaswa, zaku samu damar neman tallafin karatu guda 30 da suka kai na ₦50,000 ga kowane mutum. Waɗannan tallafin karatun an tsara su ne don a ƙara tallafawa mutanen da ke da burin cimma muradunsu a duniyar fasaha, da kuma ƙwararawa ƙwazonsu na ƙirƙira gwiwa. Shiga nan don yin rajista: https://hm.community/courses/introduction-to-web-developmenthttps://hm.community/courses/introduction-to-web-development Ku shigo a dama daku a tafiyar: Ƙofofin shiga wannan haɗakar kawo sauyin a buɗe suke sosai, suna jiranku ku shigo a rankaya daku wannan muhimmiyar tafiya. Kar ku rasa wannan kyakkyawar dama da zaku koya, ku haɓaka, da kuma gina sana'a mai 