Za a ƙaddamar da samfurin wayar CAMON 20 Doodle Edition da take da tsarukan "Anti-Shake", nan bada jimawa ba. A duniyar dake ta amon fasaha, inda tunani ya haɗu da ƙirƙira, samfurin wayar TECNO CAMON 20 Doodle ta fara ƙwace dandalin. Tushen wannan al'ajabin fasaha ya dogara ne da wani ɓoyayyen sirri, kyakkyawan murfin baya wanda aka ƙawata da tambarin doodle a jikinta, a wani haɗin gwiwa da Mr. Doodle. Bari mu natsa cikin abubuwan mamakin wannan gagarumar na'ura, yayinda muke jira a ƙaddamar da ita. Zanen Doodle a cikin duhu .: Ku shirya karɓar adon dake bayan murfin samfurin wayar CAMON 20 Doodle, wanda ke ɗauke da ƙayataccen zanen Doodle dake ƙyalli acikin duhu. Ku ƙaddara hoton kanku a cikin wurare masu duhu, ku kalla yayinda ɗan ƙaramin zanen zai riƙa ƙyalli, tare da ƙarawa wayarku abin burgewa. Da wannan zubi mara tamka, wayarku ta CAMON 20 zata zamo abar da za a riƙa hirarta a duk inda kuka je.! Kyamara mai kwaleti, mai ɗauke da fasahar Anti-Shake, da kuma fasahar Low- light Magic : Sabon samfurin wayar CAMON 20 Doodle ta dawo da kyamara mai kwaletin ɗaukar hoto da baida tamaka wajen washewa da kyau. Yi bankwana da bidiyoyi masu dishi-dishi da ɗaukar bidiyon dake cike da fasahar Anti-Shake, ɗauka mai tabbatar da kowane majigi/hoto a yanda yake. Hatta a yanayi mai ƙarancin haske, kyamararta mai fasahar low-light zata tallafa, zata baka ƙayataccen sakamako da zai baka mamaki. Abin gani na jin daɗi tare da aiki cikin sauri.! Samfurin wayar TECNO CAMON 20 Doodle, a gaskiya an gwama zane haɗe da takanolaji. Santsin jiki na zamani dake fidda sheƙi, yayinda keɓantaccen sikirin mai tsawon inci 6.9 ke bada abin kallo mai armashi, sai kuma kyakkyawan saurin aiki na 120Hz dake kore gajiyar masu sha'awar kalle-kalle, wasanni da kuma shiga shafukan intanet. Wayar, wadda kamfanin MediaTek Dimensity 8050 SoC ya samar, samfurin wayar CAMON 20 Doodle tana aiki cikin sauri na ban mamaki, tare da tallafawar RAM da yakai 16GB, da kuma memory da yakai giga bayit 256/512. Amore haɗakar kyau da ƙarfi a wannan waya mai jan hankali, aikin ƙirƙira da ya zarce tinani, da kuma ya dace da tsarin rayuwarku ta zamani. Ta Wuni da caji; ga kuma saurin yin caji: Kun damu da ƙarkon batirin waya? Da wayar CAMON 20 Doodle mai ɗauke da babban batir mai ƙarfin 5000mAh, zaku more yininku cikin sauƙi, da kuma amfani mai yawa. Kuma duk lokacin da aka tashi yin caji, caja mai saurin cajin da yakai ƙarfin 45W zata cika maka ita cikin sauri, kai dai tabbatar da kana haɗe kuma ana samun ka. Samfurin wayar TECNO CAMON 20 Doodle an tsarata ne don ta sake fasalin yanda kuke more ƙirƙira da fasaha. Saboda haka ku shirya yin tafiya data haɗa ƙirƙira da sabunta a wayar da aka tsara don ta burge. Kuci gaba da jiran ranar da za a sake ta a kasuwa, ku kuma kasance a shirye don zurfafa tunaninku tare da abokiyar tsarin rayuwa.! Zaku samu ƙarin bayanai yayinda kuka bibiyi shafin TECNO a Facebook, Instagram, da kuma Twitter.
Sabbin kamfanonin fasahar kiwon lafiya lafiya, Jumia sunzo muku da tallafin kuɗaɗe da kuke buƙata.! A ranar Talatar 17 ga watan Mayun 2022, babban kamfanin nan dake Najeriya na cinikayya ta intanet, wato Jumia, ya saki rahoton rubu'in farko na hada-hadar shekarar 2022. Shugabannin kamfanin biyu; Jeremy Hodara da Sacha Poignonnec sun bayyana cewa siyayya, rabanu, da kuma babbar darajar ciniki, sun samu gagarumar haɓaka idan aka kwatanta da rubu'ai tara da suka gabata. Idan aka kwatanta rubu'in farko na shekarar 2021 da na 2022, siyayya ta ƙaru daga miliyan 6.6 izuwa miliyan 9.3, babbar darajar ciniki kuma ta ƙaru daga dala miliyan $198.9 izuwa dala miliyan $252.7, yayinda rabanu ya tashi daga dala miliyan $33 izuwa dala miliyan $47.6. Duk da wannan cigaban, abun baiwa kamfanin yanda yake so ba, inda asarar da aka samu daga ribar kuɗin ruwa, haraji, raguwa daraja, da kuma biyan bashi wato(EBITDA) takai dala miliyan $53. A wata ziyara ga TechCrunch, Poignonnec ta bayyana cewar kamfanin na shirye-shiryen rage asarar EBITDA izuwa ƙasa da dala miliyan $70 da suka gamu da ita a rubu'in farko na shekarar 2021. Yanzu mu koma ɓangaren daddɗan labarin cigaba. JumiaPay, kamfanin su na kayan fasaha, ya fito musu wata hanyar biyan kuɗi mai lasisi ta (PSSP), wanda zai basu damar sarrafa biyan kuɗi izuwa sauran kamfanoni a Najeriya. Wannan cigaban ya sanya shi gasa kai tsaye da kamfanonin Paystack, Flutterwave, eTranzact da kuma Remita. Sun kuma samu wata hanyar ƙara samun rabanu, a lokacin da suke tsananin buƙatar ƙara yawansa. PSSP sun samun kuɗaɗensu ne ta hanyar karɓar ladan hidima daga kowanne hada-hadar kuɗi da suka asassa, waɗannan kuɗaɗen suna dogara ne da girman hada-hada. Bisa ga rahoton, kashi 34 na siyayyar da akayi a Jumia, an kammalasu ne ta hanyar amfani da hanyar biyan kuɗi ta JumiaPay, da kuma lasisinsu, JumiaPay zasu ƙara samun yawan adadin a rubu'o'i masu zuwa. Fasahar kiwon lafiya cikin gaggawa Wataƙil, abu mafi daɗi game da wannan cigaban da aka yaɗa a rahoton shine, hukuncin da Jumia suka yanke na shiga harkokin kiwon lafiya. Ta hanyar haɗa gwiwa da Consultative Group to Assist the Poor, kamfanin na gwajin wata manhaja da zata baiwa masu amfani da ita damar ganawa da likitoci ta hanyar yin rajista duk wata a dala ɗaya. Idan aka dubashi shi kaɗai, wannan wani babban yunƙuri ne da zai baiwa Jumia damar shiga cikin Kwastomominsu da kuma abubuwan more rayuwa. Zai kuma wakilci ƙarin ƙaƙƙarfan abokin gasa da tsoffin kamfanonin kiwon lafiya. Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya, ta bada shawarar kowane likita ya kamata ya riƙa duba marasa lafiya 600 ne a ƙasa, amma a Najeriya, kowane likita yana duba mutane 5,000 ne. Daɗin daɗawa, ƙungiyar likitoci ta ƙasa ta Najeriya, ta fidda wani rahoto daya nuna cewa likitoci 35,000 ne kaɗai daga cikin 72,000 da suke da rajista ke aiki a Najeriya. Yayinda sashin fasahar kiwon lafiya na Afrika ake masa shirin da zai kai dala biliyan $259 nan da shekara ta 2030. Koda yake ba ayi wani bayani mai faɗi ba dangane da yunƙurin, ƙoƙarinsu na ganin sun shiga fagen da yayi ƙaurin suna da wahala a Afrika, ba kuma shida alaƙa da kasuwancin su na nesa, ya janyo alamomin tambaya. Kafaffun kamfanonin sadar da ayyukan likitanci daga nesa da ake dasu a ƙasar sun haɗa da CribMD, iWello, da kuma WellaHealth. A matsayinsu na kamfanoni masu zaman kansu, babu bayanansu a ma'aikatun gwamnati. Amma a wata hira da Techpoint Africa a shekara ta 2021, iWell sun bada bayanin cewa sunada abokan hulɗa har guda 140. Yayinda wani rahoton ya nuna CribMD sunada marasa lafiya mutum 2,800 a shekarar ta 2021. Shugaban kamfanin WellaHealth shima ya bayyana cewar masu hulɗa da kamfanin na musamman sun kai mutum 10,000 , a shekarar 2017. Tare da wasu dubunnan a layin jira. Waɗannan kamfanonin a bayyane yake cewa ƙarfin jarinsu bai kai na Jumia ba. Yayinda sashen kiwon lafiya na Afrika ya tara dala miliyan $392 a shekarar 2021. Duk da haka,waɗannan kamfanonin dole susha fama da ƙarancin shiga yanar gizo, raguwar kuɗaɗen shiga na gidaje, da kuma ƙalubalen al'adu wajen samun abokan hulɗa da zasu biya. Daɗin daɗawa, Jumia basu da gogewa a harkar gudanarda kula da kiwon lafiya, da yiyuwar dole sai sun shiga matakin koyo idan suna son nasarar wannan yunƙuri. Duk da akwai damar da zasu iya ɗaukar ƙwararrun ma'aikata, abubuwa ba zasu gudanar musu yanda suke so ba cikin sauri. Gajeren yanayin da sashen harkar lafiya keda shi, shima wani ƙalubale ne da masu taka rawa a fagen ke fuskanta. A misali, ƴan asibitoci ƙalilan ne suke da bayanai a kwamfiyuta, kuma kaɗan ne acikinsu suma ke iya yaɗa waɗannan bayanan. Wannan yasa yake da matuƙar muhimmanci ga sabbin kamfanonin kiwon lafiya ta hanyar fasaha su samo mafita ga wannan sana'a tasu. Kafa haɗin gwiwa don samar da ingantaccen sashen kula da lafiya. Duk da cewa waɗannan abubuwan zasu iya kawo tarnaƙi ga yunƙurin Jumia na tsarin fasahar kiwon lafiya,Yomi Kazeem, wani ƙwararren masani a Salient Advisory, ya ce yayi imani cewa Jumia suna da abubuwa da ake buƙata don cimma nasara, musamman ma idan sun bi ta hanyar haɗin gwiwa. A wata ganawa da Techpoint Africa, ya bayyana cewar "Jumia zasu iya kafa tsarin fasahar kiwon lafiya daga nesa nasu, ta hanyar ƙarin haɗin gwiwa don sauƙaƙa bincike. Zasu kuma iya haɗa hannu da shagunan saida magunguna, suyi amfani da kayan aikin sadarwar su, ta hanyar haɗa kai magani da kuma gabatar da ayyukan likitanci ta nesa, Ta yanda bazai zamana marasa lafiya zasu gana da likita ne kawai daga nesa ba, a a, ya zamana ma zasu iya samun maganin da suke buƙata ba tare da wata matsala ba. Wannan sigar tana da muhimmanci, saboda gaba ɗaya idan muka ɗauka, bada damar gani da likita wani ɓangare ne guda ɗaya na harkar kiwon lafiya. Idan aka samu irin waɗannan kamfanonin suka kafu, samun masu amfani dasu zai haifar da gasa. Muhimmi dai, haɗin gwiwa da wani ɓangare zai sauƙaƙa haɗuwa da marasa lafiya masu yawa yanada matuƙar muhimmanci. Ba kamar kamfanonin fasahar kiwon lafiya da ake dasu ba, Jumia suna da rantsatstsun dabarun aiki da zasu taimaka musu gudanar da harkokin kiwon lafiya cikin sauri fiye da sabbin kamfanonin da sun dogara ne da tallafawar wani. A yayinda hakan ke nufin Jumia nada ƙwanjin kurdawa cikin kasuwa, zai kuma basu wata dama ta faɗaɗa ayyukansu na fasahar kiwon lafiya afaɗin ƙasa, alokaci guda kuma an ƙara samun wata hanyar tara rabanu ga Jumia. Sabbin kamfanonin kiwon lafiya, a misali, zasu fi samar da gamsashshen tsari kuma mai sauri idan suka haɗa gwiwa da Jumia. Irin waɗannan haɗin gwiwar zasu basu damar haɗuwa da abokan hulɗar Jumia masu ɗimbin yawa. Misali irin wannan haɗin gwiwar shine, haɗin gwiwar kamfanin sadarwa na Airtel Kenya da kamfanin MyDawa, wani shagon saida magunguna ta intanet, wanda ya baiwa Kwastomomin Airtel damar shiga shafin intanet na MyDawa ba tare da data ba, yayinda shi kuma MyDawa ya basu damar biyan kayansa da kuɗin layin Airtel. Duk da samun cigaba da annobar Covid-19 ta haifar, sabbin kamfanonin kiwon lafiya ta hanyar fasaha har yanzu sunada jan aiki a gabansu wajen cimma muradun Afrika. Duk da haka, haɗaka irin wannan zata zamo mabuɗin cigaba.
Kamfanin SeamlessHR da Gidauniyar Bill Gates sunzo da tsarin hanyoyin samun albashi ga ma'aikata a Najeriya. Kamfanin dake gaba-gaba wajen tsara hanyar biyan albashi da harkar fasahar HR, SeamlessHR, tare da haɗin gwiwar Gidauniyar Bill and Melinda Gates, a baya-bayan nan sun shirya wani taron ƙasa na leburori a wani gagarumin taro don tattauna yanda za a kyautata walwalar leburori, da kuma gudanarda aiki ta hanyar sabuwar manhaja mai laƙabin Breeze Payer. Masu gudanarwa daga Kamfanonin 7up Bottling Company, Guinness Nigeria, Lafarge Cement, Julius Berger,Bua Cement, UACN da sauransu ne suka shiga zaman tattaunawar, haka kuma sun sake shiga hirar jin ɗimi da wakilai daga Gidauniyar Bill Gates suka jagoranta, da kuma shugabanci a SeamlessHR, don samo hanyoyin warware matsalolin da ma'aikata ke fuskanta a Afrika, musamman kyautata walwala da jin daɗin ma'aikaci, da kuma inganta tsarin gudanarda aiki ta hanyar amfani da hanyoyin fasaha. A wajen tattaunawar, SeamlessHR sun gabatar da manhajar Breeze Payer, wata sabuwar manhajar masu kamfanoni, wacce zata basu damar ganowa da riƙe masu baiwa acikin ma'aikatan su, ta hanyar mafita kamar irin ta Earned Wage Access. Wannan manhaja zata baiwa masu ɗaukar leburori damar su gudanar da tsarin biyan kuɗinsu yanda ya kamata, zata sauƙaƙe biyan albashi, za kuma ta haɗa ma'aikatansu da kasuwar hidimar ƙarin darajar kuɗaɗe. Wannan kyakkyawar mafita zata baiwa ma'aikatan damar taɓa albashin su kafin ranar biya, da kuma basu damar shawo kan matsalolin kuɗi na gaggawa ba tare da cike-ciken takardu ba, a kuma farashi ƙanƙani. Daɗin daɗawa kuma, manhajar na taimakawa masu karɓar albashi damar ɗora tarihin bashi, wanda zai basu damar samun manyan basussuka masu dogon lokaci, da kuma inganta musu baki ɗaya walwalarsu ta harkokin kuɗi. Lynn Eisenhart, mataimakin Daraktan Gidauniyar Bill and Melinda, wanda yayi jawabi akan yanda jindaɗi da walwalar ma'aikata keda tasiri wajen gudanar aiki, yace, "Ma'aikata sune kadarar mu mafi muhimmanci. Mutane kan zauna ne bisa ga yanda ma'aikatu suke ta'ammali dasu, da kuma irin tagomashin da suka samu lokacin zamansu. Leburori sun cancanci a tallafa musu a sha'anin kuɗi, kuma ma'aikatunsu su tallafa musu don su ƙara hazaƙa wajen gudanar da aiki. Muna so a basu damar samun tallafin kuɗaɗe a hannunsu ta hanyar Earned Wage Access. Wannan ne yasa muka haɗa hannu da SeamlessHR da masu ɗaukar aiki, don lura da bayanan ma'aikata da kuma samar musu mafita mai ɗorewa. Anasa jawabin, shugaban SeamlessHR, Emmanuel Okeleji, yayi bayani akan mafitar fasaha da kamfanin ya gina don inganta gudanar da aikin ma'aikatu, ga masu ɗaukar aiki da ma'aikatan. A manhajar Earned Wage Access da muka ƙirƙiro, manhajar tsarin biyan albashi, wacce ta taimakawa mahukuntan Seamless wajen tafiyar da tsarin biyan albashin masu ɗaukar aiki da ma'aikata, ta kuma sauƙaƙa musu samun basuka masu ƙarancin ruwa. Haka kuma mun gina fasahar bai ɗaya ta bibiyar lokaci da kuma halartar zuwa aiki. Wannan mafita ta bai ɗaya ta sanya karsashi bisa nasarar da ta bayar a faɗin duniya, wajen tabbatar da leburori sunyi cara a wajen aiki mai mara musu baya da kuma rungumar su. Da haɗin gwiwar Gidauniyar Bill Gates da kuma manayan leburori, zamu iya yin tasiri mai ɗorewa a ɓangaren baiwar aiki a Afrika . Ƙwararren masanin fannin kimar ma'aikata Farfesa Dapo Adeleye, Daraktan Tsangayar Ilimin Ma'aikata ta Jami'ar Georgetown, babban mai maƙala a taron ya gabatar da maƙala mai kyau akan muhimmancin jin daɗin ma'aikaci, da kuma amfanin sauyawa izuwa fasaha a fagen aiki a yau. "Da buƙatar mu matsarda tunaninmu mu sake ƙimanta mas'alar ma'aikaci. A maimakon maida hankali kawai akan muhimmiyar baiwa, dolene mu gane cewa akwai kaso mai yawa na ma'aikata, wanda ya ƙunshi leburori na ƙasa-ƙasa. Zuzzurfan bincike ya nuna irin tasirin da Earned Wage Access da kuma tallafin kuɗaɗe sukayi akan ƙwazon ma'aikata . Ta hanyar fifita walwala da samar musu da kayan aiki da suka dace, zamu fito da baiwar ma'aikatanmu, da kuma jawo cigaba mai ɗorewa ga masana'antun mu.", inji shi. Sashe na biyu na taron an shirya gudanar dashi a ƙasar Kenya, yayinda SeamlessHR ke cigaba da yaɗa tasirinsu, sunyi tsayin daka da jajircewa wajen ƙarfafar kamfanoni a Afrika ta hanyar sauye-sauyen fasahar zamani. Dangane da SeamlessHR SeamlessHR wani kamfani ne da yake gaba-gaba wajen tsara hanyar biyan albashi tare da kamfanin fasahar zamani na HR, Wanda suka duƙufa wajen tallafawa kamfanoni wajen gudanar da tsarikansu na biyan albashi da HR, tun daga ɗaukar aiki har zuwa ritaya, ta hanyar sabbin hanyoyin fasahar zamani. Tare da manya da matsakaitan kamfanoni kusan 1,000 a cikin ƙasashe sama da 20, kamfanin nada ofisoshi a Najeriya, Ghana, Kenya, sai kuma ba jimawa ya fara ayyuka a Botswana. Kamfanin ba a jima ba ya tara dala miliyan $10 a Zangon A na zagayen tara kuɗaɗe don riɓanya faɗaɗa ayyukansu a Afrika, da kuma zuba sabbin kayan kuɗi, waɗanda wasunsu za a nunasu a wannan taron. SeamlessHR kamfanin fasahar zamani ne daya haɗa hannu da Gidauniyar Bill and Melinda Gates don ayyuka da suka shafi ƙananan leburori a Afrika.
Fito da baiwarka ta yin wasanni tare da wayar Infinix NOTE 30, ta hanyar amfani da fasahar Bypass Charging. Ga mayun gem a waya, don haɗuwa a shirya zagayen wasanni sanannu kamar su "Free Fire" ko "Arena of Valor", wasannin kan taimaka wajen samar da nutsuwa da kaucewa damuwa ta yau da kullum. Duk da haka, wani ƙalubale kan bijiro lokacin da cajin wayoyinsu ya ƙare yayinda suke tsaka da wasan gem, zasu buƙaci caji don cigaba da wasan. A mafi yawan lokuta hakan kan jawo ɗaukar zafi ga gama garin batiran wayoyi, wanda hakan kesa baturan suna shan wahala, saboda toshewar faifan SoC. Anyi sa a, wayar Infinix NOTE 30 tazo da maganin wannan damuwar ta hanyar fasahar bypass charging, inda take ba masu wasan gem ɗin damar yin caji yayinda suke wasansu ba tare da ɗaukar zafi ba. Da wayar NOTE 30, masu gem zasu more dogon lokacin wasa mara katsewa kuma cikin kwanciyar hankali. Wayar Infinix 30 tazo da ƙayatacciyar fasahar caji cikin sauri, inda take bada cajin yin wasanni na tsawon awa 1.95 da cajin minti biyar kacal. Daɗin daɗawa, tana caja batiri mai ƙarfin 5000mAh izuwa kaso 75% cikin mintuna 30 kacal. Wani abu da wayar tayi zarra dashi shine fasaharta ta bypass charging, wacce ke baiwa wayar wuta kai tsaye, a lokaci guda kuma tana caja batiri ana kuma wasan gem da ita. Wannan zai sa batirin ya daɗe, hana batiri tsufa da wuri, da kuma ƙarin kariya yayin da ake caji ana kuma gem. A fasahance, fasahar bypass charging wata siffa ce da wayar NOTE 30 ta keɓanta da ita. A lokacin da cajin batiri yakai ko ya wuce matsayin fara bypass charging (kaso 30% na caji), cajin zai riƙa haura batiri da tura wuta kai tsaye izuwa waya. Ta hanyar dasa mata fasahar bypass charging, wayar an rabata matsalolin ɗaukar zafi dake samun wayoyi yayinda ake caji da gem dasu lokaci ɗaya. A wani gwaji da aka gudanar a ɗakin bincike na Infinix, fasahar bypass charging ta rage matsalar ɗaukar zafi ga wayar NOTE 30 da digiri 2-7°, idan aka kwatanta da hanyoyin caji da aka saba dasu. Wannan zai yi matuƙar inganta nutsuwar mai amfani da wayar, musamman ma yayin ɗaukar dogon lokaci ana gem, ko kuma lokacin yanayin zafi. Kunna fasahar bypass charging baida wahala, za a iya samunsa ta hanyar X-Arena game interface. Masu amfani da wayar zasu iya janyo ɓangaren dama ko hagu na saman sikirin ɗin ta, sai su zaɓi kunna fasahar bypass charging. Kamfanin Infinix sun duƙufa wajen samarwa masu amfani da wayarsu ƙarin ƴanci da kuma sabbin ƙirƙira. Da wannan sabon samfurin, masu wasannin gem na iya canja matsayin bypass charging ta cikin saitin X-Arena izuwa matakai uku: matakin 20%, ko 30% ko 40%. Wanna zai ƙarfafi masu amfani da wayar su zaɓi ko wutar caji da ake kanyi, kai tsaye ta baiwa waya wuta a maimakon bi ta cikin batiri, a lokacin da batiri yakai matakin da suke so. Don morewa lokacin wasa mai armashi, jerin wayoyin NOTE 30 sunzo da keɓantacciyar manhajar wasanni ta X-Arena. Wacce ke ƙarƙashin gudanarwar ƙaƙƙarfan injin Dar-Link 2.0, cikin hazaƙa take inganta gudun CPU da GPU na injin Helio G99, don tabbatar da gudanar wasa da kuma ƙayataccen hoton kowane sashen wasa. XArena na matso da wasu alamomin kusa, kamar alamar kira da kuma tura saƙo, akwai kuma fasahar Raspawn Countdown, wacce ke baiwa masu gem damar sanin ƙirgen lokacin su na wasa, wanda zai basu damar matse ayyukan su. Wani ƙarin kuma, wayar NOTE 30 Pro takai harkokin gem izuwa wani mataki da fasahar ta VC liquid cooling, sautin flagship JBL da kuma sikirin mai ƙarfin nutsewar 120Hz, garantin babban sauti, garantin taɓi, da kuma kyakkyawan gani ga masu sha'awar gem. A yayinda zafi ya tsananta, wayar Infinix NOTE 30 na zamowa aboki mara yankewa ga masu gem, Inda take basu damar yin wasanni ba ƙaƙƙautawa ba tare da ta riƙa ɗaukar zafi ba. Ku nutse cikin duniyar wasanni mai armashi tare da abokan wasanku tsawon rana , ku kuma shige cikin annashuwar more wasanni masu ɗebe kewa tsawon lokacin zafi.! Za a iya sayen jerin wayoyin Infinix Note 30 a shagunan dillalai masu lasisi a duk faɗin Najeriya. Ku bibiyi shafin Infinix Nigeria a kafofin sadarwa na zamani don samun ƙarin bayanai akan jerin wayoyin Note 30 da kuma fasalin su mai ban ƙaye.
Fito da Ƙarfin Matasa da Al'adu da Tattalin Arziƙi na Ƙirƙire-ƙirkire: Hanya Zuwa Ga Goben Afirka - Ƙarfin Afirka The Wheatbaker, wani mashahurin otel dake zaune a Vitoria Island a garin Legas ya shaida wani gagarumin taron na manyan 'yan kasuwa, makirkira masu tasiri a Afirka, masu tsare-tsare, da zakarun fasahar dijital da kuma manyan ‘yan kasuwa daga masana’antu daba-daban ranar juma’ar da ta gabata. Waɗannan ƙwararrun mutane masu kyawawan tunani da manufa guda sun taru ne don gano yadda Afirka za ta iya tabbatar da makomarta ta hanyar fito da ƙarfin matasanta da al'adunta da tattalin arziƙinta na ƙirƙire-ƙirƙire fili. Africa Soft Power ne suka shirya tare da haɗin gwiwar gidauniyar Ford Foundation, da Open Society Foundations, tare da African Women on Board, taron ya mayar da hankali kan ƙaƙƙarfan alaƙar da ke tsakanin dandamali na dijital, ɗaukar fasahar taknoloji, ƙarfafa matasa, da ƙirƙirar kasuwanci. A matsayinta na kasa sannan kuma nahiya, yana da matukar muhimmanci a sanya mata da matasa cikin kowane rukunin shugabanci. Daga #endsars, zuwa #Congoisbleeding da sauran ƙungiyoyin zamantakewa da dama waɗanda nahiyar ta shaida a cikin 'yan shekarun nan, mun ga abin da ke faruwa idan ba mu samar da haɗin kai da tsaro da ake buƙata ga mata da matasa ba '' in ji Nkiru Balonwu, Daraktan ƙirƙire-ƙirƙire kuma wanda ya kafa Africa Soft Power. "Za mu ci gaba da yin wannan tattaunawa, tare da ba da haske kan dimbin damammakin da Africa’s Soft Power, wadanda ke da tushe mai asali a cikin al'adunta da yawan matasa, ke bayarwa don haɓaka. Nkiru ya kara da cewa “Yayin da bullowar kafafen sadarwa na zamani da ci gaban fasahar kere-kere ke samar wa matasan Afirka hanyoyin bayyana baiwarsu, da seta alkiblarsu, da gina sana’o’i masu inganci a masana’antu daban-daban, muna jajircewa wajen ci gaba da tattaunawa da za ta taimaka wa nahiyar Afirka wajen yin amfani da wannan damar ta bunkasa.” Ko da yake masana'antun ilimi da ƙirƙire-ƙirƙire suna ba da damammaki ga matasan Afirka, har yanzu akwai sauran rina a kaba ta fuskar barazanar da suke cigaba da fuskanta – wanda rashin tsaro ya kasance gaba-gaba a wannan jerin. Tsaro wani al'amari ne na tsaka-tsaki wanda ya shafi komai tun daga ainihin 'yancin ɗan adam, matsayin rayuwa, kasuwanci, cigaba, 'yancin zirga-zirga, samun damar ilimi, daidaiton jinsi, da dai sauransu. Rashin tsaro na daya daga cikin abubuwan da sukan kawo tasgaro ga cigaban ƙirƙire-ƙirƙire da bunkasar tattalin arziki a yankuna da dama na nahiyar. Taron ya ƙunshi wani zaman tattaunawa, wanda Folashade Anozie, shugaba kuma wanda ya kafa kamfanin Nonconform Productions ya jagoranta. Wakilai da kwararru kan zaman sun hada da; Njideka Agbo, Wanda ya kafa kuma Shugaban kamfanin Glann Media Consult kuma tsohon editan Mujallar Guardian Life; Hon. Akintunde Oyebode, kwamishinan kuɗi da bunkasa tattalin arzikin jihar Ekiti; Dr Seun Fakorede, Kwamishinan Matasa da Wasanni na Jihar Oyo da Adaora Ikenze, Darakta mai kula da manufofin jama'a, Anglophone West Africa a Meta. "Ba za a iya magance matsalar tsaro ba inda babu adalci" Inji Hon Akintunde Oyebode, Kwamishinan kuɗi da Ci gaban Tattalin Arziki na Jihar Ekiti." “Babban abinda ke haddasa aikata laifuka shine rashin hukunci, wannan shine dalilin da ya sa za ka ga cewa a cikin al’ummar da ba a samu hukunci ba, sau da yawa mutane sukan raja’a zuwa ga aikata laifuka. Akintunde Ya cigaba da cewa “matsalar tsaro a Najeriya matsala ce da ake fama da ita, a wasu sassan kasar nan, ana ci gaba da yin garkuwa da mutane, a wasu sassan kuma akwai matsalar shan miyagun kwayoyi, amma babban abin da ya dace shine mu yarda cewa karfin jihohi ya dade da tabarbarewa, har an kai wani matsayi da ba za a iya magance matsalolin zamantakewa ba.”. Da kusan kashi 60 na al'ummar Afirka 'yan kasa da shekaru 25, nahiyar tana alfahari da matsayinta na wadda tafi kowacce kuruciya a duniya. Nan da shekara ta 2050, hasashe ya nuna yawan jama'arta zai rubanya, inda za a sanya wannan kididdigar yawan matasa a matsayin babbar dama ta Afirka na ci gaba, ƙirƙire-ƙirƙire, da ci gaba mai dorewa. Njideka Agbo, wanda ya kafa kuma Shugaban Glann Media Consult, kuma tsohon editan Mujallar Guardian Life, ya ci gaba da cewa, rashin tsaro da rashin shigar da kowa ne ke haifar da rasa ƙwararru a Najeriya da sassan Afirka. “A baya mutane sukan yi zumudin dawowa Najeriya, amma duk abin ya canza. A shekarar 2018, mune rukuni na 4 mafi girma na masu neman mafaka a Tarayyar Turai, saboda mutane na ta ci gaba da ƙara ƙaura don neman wurare masu daɗin rayuwa da ƙarin samun damarmaki da tsaro mafi kyau. Ta kara da cewa matakin kishin kasa da matasa ke nunawa kasarsu ya dogara ne da irin kulawar da suke samu daga Gwamnati, tare da samar da tsaro da hada kai da kasar ke yi musu. Tabbatar da makoma: Ƙarfin Matasa, Al'adu da Tattalin Arzikin ƙirƙire-ƙirƙire ya kasance muhimmin dandali ga masu ruwa da tsaki na gwamnati da matasa masu murya a duk masana'antu da yawa don yin hulɗa da juna. Yayin da masu ruwa da tsaki a duniya ke nuna goyon baya ga burin Afirka, ya zama wajibi a amince da muhimmiyar rawar da karfin matasa da tattalin arzikin ƙirƙire-ƙirƙire ke takawa wajen gina nahiya mai cigaba.
Cloudax Ya Kaddamar da dandalin P2P don buƙatun Kasuwancin Cryptocurrencies a Najeriya. Yayin da Najeriya take fama da kuɗin ruwa wanda ke ƙaruwa kullum tare da ƙoƙarin karɓar kuɗin crypto a afirka, Cloudax, wani fage mai sabin salo na fasaha wanda aka samar don masu tsara bayanai a shafukan sada zumunta da al'ummomi, zai ƙaddamar da manhajarsa ta P2P App da shafinsa na yanar gizon don koyawa 'yan Afirka crypto, ta yadda za a cike giɓin buƙatar crypto ga waɗanda suke amfani da shi sau ɗaya da kuma waɗanda suke amfani da shi ko da yaushe. Da yake magana game da ra’ayin 'yan Najeriya a sararin tattaunawa kan crypto, Shugaba na Cloudax, Olumuyiwa A, ya ce "Ina ganin saurin karɓuwar cryptocurrency a Afirka ya fi jawo matsalolin da matasan Afirka ke fuskanta wajen gudanar da ayyukan kuɗi marasa iyaka yayin rayuwa da aiki. a ƙauyen duniya da duniya ta zama. Kuɗaɗen dijital sun zama hanya mafi sauƙi don gudanar da hada-hadar kuɗi kuma abin farin ciki ne ganin cewa gwamnatocin Afirka da yawa suna kokarin ko kuma suna kan hanyarsu ta samar da dokoki waɗanda zasu haɓaka amfani da cryptocurrencies a yankunansu.” A wani rahoto na 2022, Chainalysis ya nuna cewa musayar P2P tana da kashi 6% na duk adadin ma'amalar cryptocurrency a Afirka, fiye da ninki biyu na yanki mafi kusa wato Tsakiya & Kudancin Asiya da Oceania. Wannan yana nuna buƙatar ‘yan kwangila da su daidaita muhallin kasuwancin web3 da na fiat a Afirka. Ya ci gaba da cewa “Muna farin cikin gabatar da dandalinmu na P2P, wanda zai cike gibin da ke tsakanin masu sha’awar crypto da ainihin masu amfani da su a Najeriya. Manufarmu ita ce samar wa mutane mafita mara kyau kuma mai araha don ma'amalar crypto. Yayin da tsaron dukiya ya zama mafi girman abin damuwa ga yawancin masu amfani, CloudP2P ya kasance mafi kyawun wuri ga masu amfani kuma wuri mai aminci da daɗin amfani don saye da sayarwa masu sauri da sauƙi da kuma musanyawa ta crypto." Dandalin Cloud2p yana ɗauke da wasu tsare-tsare daban-daban waɗanda suka bambantashi da dandalin P2P wanda ake amfani da shi a halin yanzu. Abu na farko dai ya samar da wani yanayi mai aminci inda masu amfani zasu na saye da sayarwa da musayar kuɗaɗen crypto kai-tsaye a tsakaninsu, ba tare da buƙatar masu shiga tsakani ba. Wannan ba wai iya wahalar hada-hadar ya rage ba hattta bata lokaci wajen daidaitawa. Cloudax yana da wasu samfura wadanda ake aiki akansu, gami da kantin sauki da rangwame, da lalitar bayar da tallafi. Danna wannan link din https://app.cloudp2p.io/auth/signup?referralCode=HARRD55E don fara amfani da crypto tare da CloudP2P.
Kamfanin PATRICIA Technologies Limited ya kulla alakar haɗin gwiwa da DEIMOS Security domin kare dukiyoyin Abokan Ciniki. Patricia Technologies Limited ya shiga haɗin gwiwa tare da Deimos Cloud Security. Wannan haɗin gwiwar yana nufin kawo sauyi kan yadda kamfanin cryptocurrency ke kare dukiyoyin abokin ciniki da kyautata matakan tsaro. Ganin karuwar barazana ta yanar gizo da satar bayanai a duk duniya, kiyaye kimar abokan ciniki ya zama abu mafi mahimmanci ga kasuwanci. Patricia ta himmatu kwarai don ganin ta cimma wannan burin ta hanyar haɗin gwiwarta da Deimos Cloud Security. Ta hanyar haɗa ƙarfi, Patricia tana ɗaukar muhimmin mataki don ganin ta samar da tsaro cikakke ga abokan cinikinta. Deimos na amfani da ƙwarewa da fasaha mai girma wanda ke ƙarfafa tsarin tsaron da muke amfani da shi a halin yanzu, da kuma samar da katangar ƙarfe daga duk wani abin da ake tunanin zai iya zama barazana... Abokan cinikinmu yanzu za su iya samun kwanciyar hankali, sanin cewa dukiyoyinsu suna hannun amintattu. Wannan haɗin gwiwar yana nuna sadaukarwar Patricia ga ƙirƙira da isar da ayyuka na musamman ga abokan cinikinmu masu kima. Da yake tsokaci game da haɗin gwiwar, wanda ya kafa Patricia kuma babban jami'in gudanarwa, Hanu Fejiro, ya bayyana cewa, "Mun gane, kuma mun himmatu da kare mahimman bayanai kuma muna ci gaba da ƙoƙari wajen ganin mun yiwa ‘yan ta’addan yanar gizo fintikau. Tare da Deimos a matsayin abokin hulɗa mai mahimmanci, muna da tabbacin cewa za mu iya cimma, har ma mu dara mafi girman matakan tsaro. ". Babban Jami'in Gudanarwa na Deimos, Andrew Mori ya bayyana ra'ayinsa game da haɗin gwiwar, "A matsayinmu na abokan haɗin gwiwa na Patricia, mun himmatu wajen aiwatar da daidaitattun ayyuka na masana'antu don tsaro na girgije da kayayyakin more rayuwa. Deimos na amfani da tsare-tsaren tsaro da aka inganta da kuma ƙwarewar aiki a kan kayan Patricia na amfani da fasaha kan yanar gizo da manhaja. Tare, za mu inganta matakan tsaro, tare da tabbatar da cewa dukiyoyin abokan cinikin Patricia sun kasance cikin kariya daga duk wani lahani mai yuwuwa”. Wannan haɗin gwiwar ya nuna lokacin farin ciki ga kamfanonin biyu yayin da muke tsammanin haɗin gwiwa mai nasara wanda zai sake fasalin tsaro a zamanin na fasahar kwamfuta.
Waɗannan katunan dala na kama-da-wane za su iya taimaka muku wajen yin hada-hadar kasuwanci na duniya daga gida Najeriya. A lokacin hutu, sai da na sami sabon katin ATM da yake saura kwanaki kadan wanda ya gabata ya kare. Amma canzawar ya zo da wasu ƴan ƙalubale. Inda a baya na biya biyan kuɗade kamar na su YouTube da shi, yanzu kam ina fama. A ranar Alhamis, 5 ga watan Janairu, 2023, bankin Zenith ya sanar da abokan huldarsa cewa zai dakatar da cirar kuɗi na ATM na kasa da kasa, da hada-hadar kasuwanci ta yanar gizo, da kuma PoS da ake gudanarwa da katin naira daga ranar Litinin 9 ga watan Junairu, 2023. Ta yin hakan ne ta shiga cikin jerin bankunan Najeriya da suka rufe hada-hadar kasuwanci a kasashen duniya ta hanyar amfani da katunan naira. Tun daga shekarar 2022, da yawan bankunan Najeriya ko dai sun rage ka’idojin hada-hadar kasuwanci a ƙasashen duniya ko kuma sun rufe su gaba daya saboda yadda CBN ke ƙoƙarin dakile hauhawar farashin kayayyaki a kasar. Sai dai an samu bullowar wasu hanyoyi, musamman katunan dala, inda ‘yan Najeriya da dama ke bukatar hanyoyin biyan kuɗaɗen hada-hadar kasuwanci a kasashen duniya. Ga kaɗan daga cikin waɗannan zaɓuɓɓuka. Kula: Duka zaɓukanda aka lissafo shawarwari ne kawai, ba amincewa ba. Tabbatar cewa ka yi bincikenka kafin amfani da ɗaya daga cikin su. Payday A cikin 2021, sabuwar kamfanin fintech wato Payday, ta sanar da cewa ta rufe zagayen farko na dala miliyan 1 'yan watanni bayan ta fara aiki. Sabon kamfanin mai kishin Africa da ke amfani da salon kansa yana ba da dama ga 'yan Afirka da ke ciki da wajen nahiyar su tura kuma su karɓi kuɗi. Ta hanyar samar da asusun ajiyar kuɗi a cikin ƙasashe kamar Burtaniya da Amurka, masu amfani da ita za su iya karɓar kuɗi kamar na gida, ba tare da la'akari da inda suke ba. Masu amfani kuma za su iya ƙirƙirar katin dala wanda zai ba su damar yin sayayya har zuwa $25,000 kowane wata. Samun katin kyauta ne, amma dole ne a tantance masu amfani. Changera Kamar yadda Babban Bankin Najeriya (CBN) ya sanya iyaka kan adadin kuɗin da ‘yan Najeriya za su iya mu’amala da su, da yawa sun koma amfani da kuɗin crypto don samun damar tsallake waɗannan takunkumin. Farawar Crypto, Bitmama ya gina Changera a cikin 2021 don wannan dalili. Ta hanyar samar da katin dala mai kama-da-wane, masu amfani da Changera na iya biyan kuɗi ta kan layi tare da katin. Sauran fasalulluka sun haɗa da tura kuɗi, canjin kuɗi, da asusun banki na kama-da-wane. saɓanin sauran zaɓuɓɓukan da ke wannan jeri, Changera tana aiki da tsarin kyauta da katuttukanta. Masu amfani za su iya zaɓar tsarin kyauta, mai zaman kansa akan $50 kowace shekara, da kuma babban tsari a kan $100 kowace shekara. Masu amfani da tsarin kyauta na iya ƙirƙirar katunan kama-da-wane, amma ƙirƙirar asusun kama-da-wane na USD, GBP, CAD, ko EUR ana samar da su ne kawai ga masu amfani da tsarin mai zaman kansa ko ƙima. Chipper Cash Chipper Cash yana ɗaya daga cikin abubuwa mafiya daraja a Afirka kuma Ham Serunjogi da Maijid Moujaled suka kafa a cikin 2014. Chipper Cash yana ba da katin dala mai kama-da-wane wanda masu amfani za su iya amfani da su yayin sayayya a kan dandamali irinsu Amazon ko lokacin biyan kuɗin shiga. Samun katin kama-da-wane yana buƙatar a fara buɗe asusun Chipper Cash. Hakanan kuna buƙatar samar da hanyoyin tantancewa, kamar fasfo na ƙasa da ƙasa ko katin shaidar ɗan ƙasa. Geegpay A cikin shekaru biyar da suka gabata an samu bullowar 'yan Najeriya mazauna Najeriya da ke aiki da kamfanoni a wajen nahiyar. Amma a yayin da ya ake daɗa samun sauƙin samun waɗannan ayyukan, karɓar kuɗin aikin ba lallai ba ne ya zo da sauƙi ba. Duk da ƙarin wasu hanyoyin na karɓar kuɗi daga wajen nahiyar, hakan ya kasance ƙalubale. Geegpay samfur ne na Raenest wanda aka yi domin ma'aikatan masu zaman kansu a Afirka. Ta hanyar Geegpay, ma'aikata masu zaman kansu na iya karɓar kuɗinsu su kuma samar da takardar shaidar biyan kuɗi. Haka nan zasu samu asusun dalar Amurka da katin dala na kama-da-wane. Samun katin dala na kama-da-wane na cin $2 kuma hakan na iya yiwuwa ne kawai bayan mai amfani ya kammala duk hanyoyin yin rajista da tabbatarwa. Za a buƙaci ku bayar da cikakkun bayanai kamar aikin ku, bayanan ma'aikata, shaidar adreshi, da katin shaida, don haka tabbatar da cewa kuna da su a hannu. Wani sabon kamfanin Najeriya, Raenest, yana son taimaka wa 'yan Afirka a ɗauke su aiki a kuma biyan su a ko'ina ALAT . Wanda mafi yawan lokatu ake kiranta da cikakken bankin dijital na farko a Najeriya, ALAT shine reshen fintech na bankin Wema. An kafa shi a cikin 2017, ALAT yana ba da cikakkiyar ƙwarewar banki ta dijital don abokan cinikinta sama da 700,000. Masu amfani da ALAT na iya ƙirƙirar sabon asusu a ƙasa da mintuna biyar, wanda zai ba su damar samun lamuni da dandamalin tanadi na atomatik. Hakanan yana ba da jerin katuna waɗanda ke sauƙaƙa biyan kuɗi gida da waje. Katin kiredit ɗin dalar sa da katunan dala na kama-da-wane suna taimaka wa masu amfani da shi don biyan kuɗi, gami da YouTube yayin biyan sabis a kan gidajen yanar gizo na duniya. Eversend Eversend ya samar da katunan kama-da-wane ga masu amfani tun 2020, wanda ke ba su damar biyan sabis a kan dandamali kamar Aliexpress, Amazon Prime, Spotify, Skillshare, da Namecheap. Bude katin kama-da-wane a kan Eversend kyauta ne, amma masu amfani suna biyan kuɗin kulawa na $1 kowane wata. Haka nan dole ne su saka kuɗi $1 a katin, yayin da ana iya buɗe katunan da yawa. Za a iya saka kuɗi a katin yanar gizo na Eversend ta hanyar tura kuɗi daga asusun banki ko ta kuɗin wayar hannu ko ta hanyar amfani da katin hada-hadar kuɗi. Shin kuna mu'amalar kuɗi ta ƙasa-da-ƙasa a wasu lokutan? Da wace hanyar biyan kuɗi kuke amfani? Yi bayani a sashen tsokaci.
An ƙaddamar da Global Tech Africa tare da haɗin guiwar NITDA da U.S. Consulate General, Lagos Abuja – Global Tech Africa (GTA), wani yunƙuri na Gidauniyar Future Map Foundation wanda Ascend Studios Foundation ta tsara kuma ta aiwatar; tare da haɗin gwiwar Hukumar Bunkasa Fasahar Sadarwa ta Kasa (NITDA) da Ofishin Jakadancin Amurka da ke Legas sun kaddamar a Najeriya. An tsara taron ne don tara masu ruwa da tsaki na Afirka da na ƙasa da ƙasa a fannin Tech, buɗe damar samun bunƙasuwa, da gina fasahar ƙere-ƙere a Afirka. Sauran abokan haɗin gwiwa sun haɗa da Business Sweden, Garden Group, RivExcel Health da sauran katafarun kamfanonin Fasaha a duk faɗin duniya. Ana sa ran Afirka za ta taka muhimmiyar rawa a duniyar fasaha ta hanyar samar da ƙirƙire-ƙirƙire da baiwa da sabin damarmakin kasuwanci a fannoni irinsu fasahar wayar hannu da kasuwanci ta yanar gizo da fasahar hada-hadar kuɗi da fasahar harkokin noma da tattalin arziƙi na na'ura da yanar gizo. Darakta Janar na NITDA, Inuwa Kashifu Abdullahi ya jaddada damar da GTA za ta iya kawowa Afirka inda Najeriya zata taka muhimmiyar rawa wajen bunkasa ci gaban fasahar ƙere-ƙere ta Afirka “Kwarewar fasahar Najeriya zata kunna fitilar da zata haska fasahar ƙirƙire-ƙirƙire a Afirka ta hanyar samun ci gaba mai inganci na dijital a nan gaba, inganta samar da ayyukan yi da bunƙasar tattalin arziki a faɗin nahiyar. Ƙasar ta hau kan hanyar zama babban fagen fasahar na'ura da yanar gizo a Afirka ta hanyar amfani da matasan ƙasar masu sha'awar fasaha da dokoki masu kyau. Ƙasar Amirka ta kasance babbar abokiyar haɗin guiwa ga Nijeriya wajen samar da kyakkyawan yanayi ga fasahar ƙere-ƙere. “Tawagar Amurka ta Najeriya za ta ci gaba da inganta kawancen da zai haɓaka fasahar ƙere-ƙere da samar da sabbin kyakkyawan muhallai ga sabbin kamfanoni a Najeriya, don ci gaban fasaha da inganta dangantakar kasuwanci da saka hannun jari tsakanin Amurka da Najeriya. Najeriya tana samun karbuwa cikin hanzari ga Kamfanonin fasaha na duniya a matsayin cibiyar kwarewa da fasaha da ƙirƙire-ƙirƙire, kuma Ofishin Jakadancin Amurka ya kuduri aniyar yin aiki tare da kamfanonin fasahar Amurka da na Najeriya don amfana da wannan babbar dama." - Jakadan Amurka Will Stevens. Za a gudanar da taron GTA a Legas ranar 25 ga Yuli 2023 tare da masu ruwa da tsaki 300 daga kamfanonin fasaha masu zaman kansu, na gwamnati, da sassan ci gaba. Taron zai biyo bayan taron GTA a birnin Lagos na Najeriya tsakanin ranakun 17 zuwa 20 ga watan Nuwamba 2023. Yayin bayani game da irin damarmakin da GTA zai bai wa mahalarta, Dr. Inya Lawal, shugaban Ascend Studios Foundation kuma mai aiwatar da ayyukan GTA, da Abdulsalam Umar, shugaban Future Map sun tabbatar da cewa GTA zai samu tallafi daga fannoni masu zaman kansu da na gwamnati da na ayyukan kawo ci gaba don samar da damarmaki kan masu harkokin fasaha da tallafa wa sabbin kamfanoni da zuba kuɗin buɗe kamfani, kamar dai yadda yake kuma tabbatar da ƙarin samun damar shiga da haɓaka Duniyar Mata Masu Fasaha. Taron na GTA zai samar da wani dandali ga masu ruwa da tsaki da suka haɗa da masu saka jari, masu kula da harkokin kasuwanci, masu sayen kayayyaki, malaman jami’a, da sauran jama’a, don shiga tattaunawa da kuma lalubo damarmaki na haɗin guiwa don tsara makomar fasahar Afirka. Taron ya ƙunshi sassa kamar haka, sashen farawa, karkasa mahalarta, gasa, bayyana ababe, alaƙa ta gefe, da cin abinci. Bayyana damar da ke cikin Dokar Kafa Sabbin kamfanoni ta Najeriya da kuma abubuwan da ta bayar, da GTA a matsayin taron ƙungiyar taron koli da sauran tarurruka zasu ba da dama ga masu zuba jari, masu mulki, da 'yan kasuwa don gano zuba jari da damar haɗin guiwar duniya. GTA za ta samar da wani dandali ga masu amfani, masu sha'awa, da jama'a baki daya don yin hulɗa tare da koyo daga masana fasaha da kwararru- baje kolin sabbin fasahohi a Afirka da kuma ba da haske game da sabbin abubuwa da zasu so a gaba.
Gamic da Scalex suna Ƙarfafa Masu Amfani na Afirka da damar siye da siyar da Crypto cikin Sauƙi akan manhaja. A duniyar crypto mai ban ƙaye da hanyoyin hada-hadar kuɗin da bata da mai tsari guda ɗaya, wani abu mai ban sha'awa ya faru. Gamic da Scalex sun haɗa ƙarfi don samar da kyakkyawar mafita ga 'yan Afirka waɗanda ke son siye da siyar da crypto a kuɗinsu na gida. Wannan haɗakar ta jawo wasu damarmaki a duniyar Web3, tana mai sauƙaƙawa mutane shiga duniyar crypto. Menene wannan sabon fasalin na musamman? A kan manhajan hira na Gamic, yanzu zaku iya ba da kuɗin walat ɗin ku na Web3 kai tsaye tare da fiat kuma ku janye kai tsaye zuwa asusun bankin ku cikin sauƙi. Gamic da Scalex sun taru don samar da wani fasali na musamman wanda ke ba ka damar saka kuɗi cikin sauƙi a cikin walat ɗin crypto (ajiya), ko cire kuɗi daga ciki (cire) a cikin kuɗin gida, kamar Naira. Me yasa wannan fasalin yake da matukar mahimmanci? Ga mutane da yawa a Afirka, samun damar amfani da cryptocurrencies na iya zama da wahala. Amma Gamic da Scalex suna canza wannan ta hanyar gina kayan aiki da ayyukan da zasu taimaka muku wajen samun kwarin gwiwa da ƙima a duniyar Web3. Da wannan haɗin gwiwar, yanzu an ƙara samun sauƙi wajen amfani da kuɗin crypto da kuma gano abubuwa masu ban sha'awa da za su iya yi don masu ƙirƙira da al'ummomi da 'yan kasuwa. Bincika GameFi, NFTs, Metaverse, da DeFi Abu mafi kyawu a wannan haɗin gwiwar shine yana buɗe ƙofafin abubuwa masu ban mamaki kamar GameFi, NFTs, Metaverse, da DeFi. Waɗannan na iya zama masu rikitarwa amma kada ku damu, Gamic yana sauƙaƙa muku siye, riƙewa da siyar da kadarorin dijital kamar katin kuɗin crypto da NFTs, da kuma cire kuɗin da kuka samu na crypto daga wasanni, tambayoyin da iska mai saukar ungulu na al'umma ba tare da damuwa ba. Canza Crypto din ku cikin Sauƙi Wani Babban abin lura shine cewa zaku iya musanya kuɗin crypto cikin sauƙi. Wannan yana nufin zaku iya canza su daga wannan nau'in zuwa wancan cikin sauri. Wannan yana buɗe kyawawan damammaki masu yawa a gare ku don haɓaka crypto ku kuma gwada kudaden dijital daban-daban. Mayar da abin da ake samu na Crypto zuwa kuɗin gaske Idan kuna son yin wasanni akan Gamic ko samun silallan crypto airdrops, za ku yi farin ciki da sanin cewa yanzu zaku iya juya kuɗin da kuke samu na crypto zuwa kuɗin gaske! Wannan yana nufin zaku iya amfani da shi domin siyan abubuwa, biyan kuɗi, ko tallafawa al'ummar ku. Kamar maida abinda ake yi don nishaɗi ne zuwa abu mai daraja! Watau; Wannan haɗewar babban ci gaba ne, musamman ga 'yan Afirka waɗanda ke son bincika cryptocurrencies. Da fasalin siye da sayar da crypto/cinikayya, zaku iya sakawa ku kuma cire kuɗi cikin sauƙi a cikin kuɗin gida. Wannan yana nufin yanzu zaku iya shiga wurare masu kayatarwa kamar su GameFi, NFTs, Metaverse, da DeFi ba tare da matsala ba. Bugu da ƙari, za ku iya canza crypto ɗinku cikin sauri, har ma ku iya canza kuɗin da kuke samu a wasa zuwa kuɗin gaske.! Wannan dama ce mai kyau ta ci gaba da ƙarfafawa kan harkokin kuɗi. Da Gamic da Scalex suna kan gaba, yi shirin shiga kyakkyawar makomar Web3 a Afirka! Fara a nan: https://gamic.app/s/000m000Y
Ranar Cin Kasuwar Crypto: Fa'idoji da Dabarun Samun Riba Cikin Ƙanƙanin lokaci. Idan ana maganar kuɗin crypto ne, samun riba, da kuma dabarun kasuwanci, to saka ni a tafiyar cikin sauri! Idan kaima irina ne, zan saka ne a cikin kasuwar ranar crypto. Wannan yana ɗaya daga cikin sanannun dabarun kasuwanci, kuma in anbi hanyar da ta dace, zaka iya yin kasuwanci don samun riba cikin sauri. Ko kai farin shiga ne ko ɗan kasuwa mai cin kasuwar kaka, zaka samu ɗan abin kamawa a waɗannan bayanan. Ka shirya samun ƙaruwa a ranar cin kasuwar crypto? Bari mu faro daga tushe. Mecece ranar cin kasuwar crypto? Idan Muka Koma Daga Tushe Ranar cin kasuwa bai taƙaita ga iya crypto ba. Ma'ana ce da take sananniya tun a tsarin kasuwancin gargajiya na da, kamar hannayen jari, canjin kuɗaɗe, da kuma sauran kayayyaki. Cin kasuwar yini guda na nufin shiga da kuma fita daga kasuwa a rana ɗaya. Cin kasuwar yini guda tazo ne daga kasuwar hannayen jari, saboda ana iya gudanar da kasuwanci ne a lokacin cin kasuwa, saboda haka duk hada-hadar da aka ƙulla za'a kammalata ne a wannan ranar. Zaka iya jin "kasuwancin yini guda" a cikin waɗannan jawabai , amma karka damu, duk ɗaya ne da kasuwar yini guda. Abinda ake magana akai shine, cin kasuwar crypto ta rana ɗaya na nufin saye da sayar da hajar crypto a yini guda, tare da samun riba, saboda armashin kasuwa. Ɗaya ne daga cikin hanyoyin musayar crypto masu tsoka. Ranar cin kasuwar crypto ɗayace daga cikin ranakun da ake amfani da armashin kasuwar crypto don samun ƙaruwa. Ana ribatar saurin tashin farashin kasuwar don samun riba ga ƴan kasuwa, amma kuma ba ƴar canke bace; caca ce kawai. A kasuwar crypto ta yini ɗaya, yanada muhimmanci ka shiga da dabarun cin nasara, wanda zamu ɗan kalla. Matakan da Za a Bi Don Cin Kasuwar Crypto: Shiryarwa Ga Farin Shiga Kasan Kasuwar Bai kamata ka shiga kasuwa ba tare da samun cikakken wayar da kai ba. Saboda haka, ka faro daga tushe ta hanyar ilmantar da kanka game da crypto, dabarun fasahar tara su, da kuma abubuwan da suke shafar farashi da canjawar kasuwa. Misali, samfurin utility crypto yafi haɗarin gamuwa da asara akan samfurin crypton dake tafiya a rarrabe da manhaja, wato (DApp). Ka bi ƙwararrun harkar, shiga cikin ayarin ƴan crypto, ka kuma riƙa zurfafa karatu akan fannin kafin ka aikata. Zaɓi sahar yin Musaya Da buƙatar ka zaɓi shafin yin musaya, inda zaka riƙa shiga da fita daga kasuwar cikin sauri. Muhimman abubuwan la'akari yayin zaɓin shafin yin musaya sun haɗa da cajin kuɗin hada-hada, motsin kadara, (shine... cikin wane irin ƙanƙanin lokaci zaka sauya kadarar ka izuwa kuɗi), da kuma lokacin gudanar da hada-hada. Idan kai ɗan kasuwa ne a Najeriya ko Ghana, zaka iya amfani da sanannun shafukan musaya kamar irinsu Binance da Coinbase don ka siya. Duk da haka, don ficewa daga cikin kasuwa cikin sauri da kuma riƙe darajar kuɗin crypto, shafin Breet shine mafi kyawun shafin da zaka saida crypton ka. Ka yanke shawarar akan dabarun kasuwanci. Ranar cin kasuwar crypto ba kawai akan nishaɗi da murna ba. Harka ce mai cike da lissafi da dabarun samun riba. Ƴan kasuwan dake yin nasara sunada gajerun dabarun kasuwanci, wanda suka haɗa da sanin lokutan shiga da ficewa daga kasuwa, dabarun tsaida asara, da kuma tsarin kaucewa haɗari. Suna kuma amfani da wasu dabarun sanin makama dake taimaka musu wajen yanke hukunci da faɗaɗa ayyukansu. Ga wasu kyawawan dabaru da zaka iya amfani dasu don cin kasuwar yini mai cike da riba Dabaru Mafiya Kyau Na Cin Kasuwar Crypto Ta Rana Ta farko itace High-Frequency Trading (HFT) High-Frequency Trading wata hanya ce ta amfani da manhajar bots don cin kasuwar crypto cikin sauri kamar walƙiya. Manhajar ta ƙunshi hanyoyin ƙiyasta kasuwa, gane alƙiblar kasuwa, da kuma yin cinikayyar ka yanda ya kamata don samun riba cikin ƙanƙanin lokaci. Kasuwar tana gudana da sauri matuƙa, amma ƙaƙƙafar manhajar bots zata iya bin saurin nata, ta kuma gane alƙiblar da tasa gaba da kuma wadda ta bari cikin ƴan sakanni. Saboda cigaban ƙere-ƙeren fasaha, manhajar HFT ta zamo sananniyar dabarar kasuwanci. Manhajar HFT tana gudanar da kasuwanci da karan kanta, inda take kammala ciniki da zarar taga hajar da ta cika sharuɗɗan da mai saye ya shimfiɗa. Manhajar HFT kan siyi haja ya siyar da ita cikin sauri don samun riba. Arbitrage hanya ce ta siyen crypto a wani shafi a kuma saida shi a wani, duk da ɗan bamabancin farashi don samun ƴar riba. Kasuwancin crypto ta manhajar High-Frequency Trading yafi, saboda yana sa kuɗi yaci gaba da mazayawa yana kuma haɗa masu siye da masu siyarwa cikin sauri, don tabbatar da dattaku. Na'urar da ake dasa HFT tana baiwa ƴan kasuwa damar ƙara ninka rabarsu, saboda ana gudanar da hada-hadar ne akan ƙa'idojin da ƴan kasuwar suka sanya. Gajeriyar Cinikayya Ana gajeriyar cinikayya ne lokacin da ƴan kasuwa suka ƙyale kadarori masu yawa a kasuwa, amma suka ribaci motsin ƙaramin farashi a kasuwar maimakon babban farashi. Manufar itace a tara ƙaramar riba mai yawa a kasuwancin rana ɗaya, don samun gwaggaɓar riba a ƙarshen kasuwar. A gajeriyar cinikayya, coin ɗin da yake armashi anfi sayen sa da zuba masa kuɗi da yawa, kamar Bitcoin, saboda caccanjawar motsin farashi. Don faɗaɗa riba, masu yin gajeriyar cinikayya kan ƙirƙiro buƙatunsu, da kuma samar da kayan ta hanyar siyansu a farashin da aka musu. A gajeriyar cinikayya amfi kallon dabarun ƙididdiga akan dabarun shimfiɗa, saboda haka ƴan kasuwa da suka dogara da wannan hanyar sun san sirrin yanda sahar crypto ke aiki, sun kuma san yanda zata juya tayi armashi a kowane irin hali. Gajeriyar cinikayya ana iya yinta kai tsaye ta amfani da manhajar kasuwanci ta bots, don samo ciniki mai armashi da kuma riba. Daɗin daɗawa, saboda muhimmancin motsin kuɗi, cikin gaggawa ake tsaida abinda zai janyo asara. A saboda haka bata kamaci sabon shiga ba. Cinikin Da'ira Kamar yanda muka sani, farashin crypto yana ƙunshe ne a cikin wata da'ira. Farashin kan iya hawa, yakan kuma iya saukowa, akan nuna hakan a layin mara baya, da layin jajircewa . A duk sanda ya haura ko ya sauka daga wannan da'irar, hakan manuni ne na sauyin da ba a saba gani ba. Masu cinikin da'ira na amfani da wannan hanyar wajen yanke lokacin da yafi dacewa su saya ko su sayar da kadarar su. Idan suna matakin mara baya, farashin crypto bai cika yin armashin da zai yo ƙasa ba. A kuma sanda yake kan matakin jajircewa, farashin crypto kan iya haɗuwa da tarnaƙin da zai iya hana shi hauhawa. Saboda haka, idan farashin na kusa da matakin mara baya, wannan shine mafi kyawun lokacin da ya dace mutum ya shiga kasuwa ya kuma fice, lokacin da farashin ke dab da matakin jajircewa. Kasadar Cikin Cin Kasuwar Crypto Ta Rana Guda Kasuwar crypto na iya yin armashi. Duk da haka, takan zo da abubuwan yin taka tsantsan, kuma sakamakon kan iya zama mummuna idan mutum bai lura da waɗannan kasadar dake cikin kasuwar crypto ba. Rashin Daidaito Kasuwar crypto tayi ƙaurin suna wajen rashin tabbas da ƙin ɗaukar hasashen yanayin farashi. Coin ɗaya na iya yin daraja yau, gobe kuma ya karye. Saboda haka idan kai sabon shiga ne a kasuwar crypto, zaka sha wahala wajen fama da yanayin ta. Amma ƙwararrun ƴan kasuwa sun san ya take, sukan ma yi amfani mabambantan dabaru su juya ta yanda zasu mora. Ƙiyasi Mai Cike Da Ƙura Ba ayi gamsashshen bayanin tsawon lokacin da kasuwar crypto zata ɗauka tana ci ba. Ba kamar kasuwar hannun jari ba, wacce take tana da tsarin kasuwanci da kuma bayanannen tsarin cigaban kuɗi da aka gina shi akan ƙoƙarinsu na kasuwa, kasuwar crypto batada wannan. Hatta coins ɗin da suke da muhimmanci a duniyar fasaha sukan zo da ƙalubalen kasa nazartar dogon lokacin da zasu iya ɗauka a kasuwar — abinda yasa yake da matuƙar wahala a iya hasashen farashin su. A kasuwar crypto, kawai abinda ka gani, shi ka samu. Ba Wasu Shimfiɗaɗɗun Ƙa'idoji Wasu zasu yabi kasuwar crypto saboda wannan, yayinda wasu kuma za suyi ɗari-ɗari da ita saboda haka. A zahiri, wannan sha'ani ne na fahimta. Rashin dokokin bai ɗaya ya baiwa mutane ƴancin ƙashin kai akan kuɗaɗen su, ya kuma basu damar su gudanar da kasuwanci duk ta yanda suka ga dama. A lokaci guda kuma, ta kan iya zama wani sarari ga mugayen mutane da baza su fuskanci hukunci ba, saboda babu wata doka data bada damar a hukunta su. Sai dai munga cigaba mabambanta a mabambantan ƙasashe dake ƙoƙarin ganin sun shimfaɗawa crypto dokoki. Ƙasar Amurka misali, a yanzu tana kan wannan ƙoƙari da ƙudirori masu dama, yayinda ƙasashe irinsu El Salvador su gaba ɗaya ma sun karɓi Bitcoin a matsayin halastaccen kuɗi. Saboda haka mabambantan labarai ne ga mabambantan mutane. Duk da muna cigaba da ganin ƙa'idoji a sahar crypto, Kai ne dai kake da cikakken ikon tsaron kanka da kuma gudanar da dukiyar ka. Kammalawa. Kasuwar Crypto ta rana guda nada matuƙar riba mai maiƙo da kuma kusanci, tare da kyakkyawar ilmantarwa akan waɗannan dabarun na: High-Frequency Trading, Scalping ko Range Trading, zaka iya samun nasarar cin riba a kasuwar. Kasa a ranka acewq kasuwar crypto na tafiya ne cikin sauri matuƙa, saboda haka dole kaima kayi sauri kamar yadda take yi. Kuma idan lokacin da zaka amshi ribarka yayi, zaka iya damƙa yardar ka ga shafin Breet don musaya mai kyau ba tare da asarar ƙima ko ɗaya ba a cikin kuɗin. Canja crypto izuwa tsabar kuɗi baida wahala a shafin Breet, da wuya ka motsa yatsanka da saitin Automatic Settlement, zasu sanya maka tsabar kuɗinka a asusun ka na banki a Najeriya ko a Ghana.! Fatan nasara, yayinda kuke kutsawa cikin waɗannan sirrikan cinikayyar crypton don samun riba a rana ɗaya. Ayi kasuwancin lafiya.!
Ƙungyar Grooming Endowment Trust tare Ƙungiyar Kickoff Africa sun Fara Kashi Na Biyu na shirin GETAccelerated, Wani Shiri ne da ke Bawa Kamfanoni Masu Tasowa Damar Samun Tallafin N10,000,000 Kyauta. Ƙungiyar Grooming Endowment Trust (GET) - tare da haɗin gwiwar Ƙungiyar Kickoff Africa, sanannun masu tallafawa ƙananun kasuwanci masu tasowa na 'yan kasuwa a Afirka - na ƙira ga masu son samun kashi na biyu na shirin GETAccelerated; yunƙurin kawo sauyi da aka tsara don ƙarfafa masu ƙirƙira a matakin farko a Najeriya. Shirin GETaccelerated yana bawa zaɓaɓɓun sabbin kamfanoni damar samun N10,000,000 a kyauta, tare da samun ƙwararrun masu ba da shawara da damar kasuwa masu ƙima. Ƙungiyar Grooming Endowment Trust (GET) ƙungiya ce mai zaman kanta da aka kafa don inganta ci gaban zamantakewa mai dorewa ta hanyar ilimi, lafiya, kasuwanci, da ci gaban al'umma. Tare da mayar da hankali kan bayar da tallafi da saka hannun jari a kyauta ga kamfanonin al'umma, ƙungiyar GET na da nufin haifar da tasiri mai kyau da kuma ƙarfafa mutane da al'ummomi a Najeriya. Ƙungiyar GET tare da haɗin gwiwar KickOff Africa sun aiwatar da bugu na farko na shirin GETAccelerated a shekarar 2022 tare da tallafawa masu ƙirƙira a matakin farko guda 10 ta hanyar sanya hannun jari na N10,000,000 kyauta, sannan sun fara kashi na biyu na shirin na 2023. Ƙungiyar GETAccelerated ta shirya tallafawa sabbin kamfanoni da ke aiki a muhimman ɓangarori kamar hidimar kuɗaɗe, kiwon lafiya, ilimi, aikin noma, abubuwan more rayuwa na dijital (tattalin arziki), tasirin zamantakewa, kafofin watsa labarai, sufuri/safara kayayyaki, da kasuwanci (kasuwanci ta yanar gizo ko kasuwancin al'umma). Bayan zazzafan aikin tantancewa da tsarin zaɓe, sabbin kamfanoni goma ne za su sami jimillar kuɗi ₦55 miliyan kyauta, da samun dama ga ƙwararrun masu ba da shawara, da damammaki na kasuwa don inganta kasuwancinsu. Domin cancanta, dole ne ya zama an yiwa sabbin kamfanoni rajista kuma a haɗa su da Hukumar Kula da Kamfanoni (CAC), suna da mafi ƙarancin samfuri (MVP) tare da wasu masu amfani ko masu biyan kuɗi, kuma sun kasance suna aiki na tsawon watanni 6 zuwa shekaru 2. Bugu da ƙari, ya kamata tsarin kasuwancinsu na musamman ya haifar kai tsaye ko a kaikaice da wani nau'i na tasiri kan ( zamantakewa, tattalin arziki, tattalin arzikin al'umma, siyasa) a cikin al'ummomi. Sabbin kamfanoni da wannan matakin, matakin farko, ko mataki na biyu duk ana ƙarfafa musu gwiwa su nema. “Mun yi farin cikin gudanar da kashi na biyu na shirin GETAccelerated da kuma samar wa waɗanda suka yi ƙirƙira a matakin farko kayyakin da suke buƙata don bunƙasa kasuwancinsu. Gami da bayar da kuɗi kyauta, jagoranci, da damar kasuwanci, mun yi imanin cewa wannan shirin zai kasance mai kawo sauyi na haɓakawa da ƙirƙire-ƙirƙire ga sabbin kamfanoni masu tasowa na 'yan Najeriya." - Michael Adoghe; Manajan Ayyuka, ƙungiyar Grooming Endowment Trust. Mun fara sanin yadda tallafawa 'yan kasuwa ke haifar da ƙarin dama da tasiri a cikin al'ummomin da ke fuskantar wariyar launi, ta hanyar kashi na farko na shirin GETAccelerated. Muna sa ran tallafawa ƙirƙire-ƙirƙire da dama a Najeriya, ta hanyar ba wa sabbin kamfanoni damar samun jari, jagoranci da kayayyaki da ake buƙata don gudanar da aiki mai wahala na warware matsalolin da ke ci gaba da ɗorewa a Najeriya” - Fola Olatunji-David; Ɗaya daga cikin masu Ƙirƙira, KickOff Africa Haɗin gwiwar ƙungiyar Kickoff Afirka da ƙungiyar GET tun lokacin da aka fara shirin GETAccelerated ya kasance mai amfani yayin da ƙungiyar Kickoff Afirka ta shahara saboda tallafinta ga ƙirƙire-ƙirƙire a duk faɗin Afirka da kuma saka hannun jarinta ga sabbin kamfanoni a matakin farkon, kuma yana da kyakkyawan matsayi don ba da jagora mai muhimmanci da ƙwarewa ga 'yan kasuwa masu shiga. Shirin GETAccelerated ya kuma ƙara gayyatar masu ƙirƙira a mataki na biyu don zaman tattaunawa kai tsaye yanar gizon a ranar Juma'a, 21 ga watan Yuli, 4pm-5:30pm, wanda zai samu halartar ƙwararrun kan masana'antu Toyin Bamidele (Manajan 