Katin RightCard ya samu Lasisin IMTO daga Babban Bankin Ƙasa na Najeriya. Kamfanin RightCard Payment Services Limited, wani reshe ne na kamfanin Lemonade Technology Inc., na alfaharin sanar da cewa ya samu lasisin gudanarwa na Hukumar Kula da Masu Aikin Tura Kuɗaɗe ta Duniya daga Babban Banki Ƙasa na Najeriya. Wannan gagarumin ci gaban na nuni da jajircewar kamfanin Lemonade Technology Inc wajen gudanar da amintantu kuma wadatattun ayyuka ta hanyar bin ƙa'idojin da Babban Bankin Ƙasa na Najeriya ya gindaya. A matsayin ma'aikaci da ke da lasisin IMTO a Najeriya, yanzu kamfanin RightCard Payment Services zai iya haɗaka kai tsaye da bankuna, ba tare da 'yan tsakiya ba wanda hakan zai samar da mafi kyawun tsari ga abokan ciniki da ke tura kuɗaɗe zuwa Najeriya. Kamfanin LemFi ya riga ya samu a matsayin Cibiyar Kuɗi ta Na'ura tare da Ikon Samar da Kuɗaɗe a Burtaniya. Yana mai ƙari kan nasararsa da gwanintarsa a duniya , kamfanin RightCard yana kawo sabbin canje-canje na dijital zuwa abokan ciniki a kasuwanni daban-daban ta hanyar manhajar LemFi. LemFi manhaja ce mai sauƙin amfani, gami da ragi mai rahusa da ma'amaloli masu sauri, ya sanya shi abin da aka fi so ga miliyoyin abokan ciniki a cikin Ingila, Kanada da Amurka. Yayin da yake bayani kan neman lasisi, Manajan manhajar LemFi na Ƙasa, Dalapo Omaroso, ya ce, "Muna farin cikin cewa RightCard ya samu karɓar lasisinsa na CBN, hakan kuma shaida ne game da jajircewarmu da dogewa wajen hidimtawa kasuwannin Najeriya. Wannan babban ci gaba yana ƙarfafa matsayinmu na masu jagorantar Aikin Musayar Kuɗi na Ƙasa da Ƙasa kuma yana nuna burinmu na ƙarfafa mutane ta hanyar samar da ayyuka masu tsari, amintattu, da araha na musayar kuɗi." Idan kuna buƙatar ƙarin bayani da sabbin bayanai, kuyi ƙoƙari ku ziyarci adireshinmu na yanar gizon a www.lemfi.com ko kuyi mana aike ta "compliance@lemfi.com" Kasance tare da mu a wannan tafiya mai ban sha'awa kuma ku kasance tare da sabbin labarai da ci gaba ta hanyar bin mu akan kafofin watsa labaru da tuntuɓar ƙungiyar tallafin mu. Mun gode da ci gaba da goyon bayanku.
Manhajar Tech1M Yayi Kaddamarwa a Kamfanin Founders Connect, Yana mai Ƙarfafa Tsarin Ɗaunkan Ma'aikata don Kasuwanci a Duniya Tech1M, manhajar AI ne na kasuwanci don tantance masu hazaƙa a duniya kuma ɗaya daga cikin masu tallafawa kanun labarai a babban shirin Founders Connect na kai tsaye, ya ƙaddamar da samfurin tsarin ɗaukan ma'aikata a duniya mai ciki da sauyi. Tare da fitowar sabon samfurinsa, manhajar Tech1M an saitata don sake fasalta ma'auni na ɗaukar ma'aikata, yana baiwa kasuwanci mafita mara misaltuwa don tantancewa, ɗaukar ma'aikata, da biyan masu hazaƙa a duniya. A kwanakinnan manhajar Tech1M tare da goyon bayan manhajar Techstars ta J.P. Morgan, ya ba da damar taron yayin da yake ba da ingantaccen dandali don gabatar da sabbin samfuransa ga kasuwannin Afirka. Samfurin AI na manhajar Tech1M yana magance matsalolin game da tantancewa da kuma ɗaukan ma'aikata da fiye SMEs miliyan 400 ke fuskanta a duniya. Ta hanyar tantancewa da ɗaukan masu hazaƙa daga ko'ina a duniya, manhajar Tech1M yana bawa 'yan kasuwa damar ɗaukan ma'aikata da sauri ninki shida, da sauƙaƙaƙƙen farashi mai inganci, kuma a yalwacei, duk a cikin dandali ɗaya. A cikin abubuwan da ta gabatar a lokacin taron, wacce ta ƙirƙiri manhajar Tech1M, Tommie Edwards, ta faɗakar da masu ƙirƙira da masu hazaƙa kan ikon manhajar Tech1M na tantancewa da kulawa yadda ya kamata wajen biyan masu hazaƙa a duniya. A cewar Tommie Edwards, "manhajar Tech1M ba kawai yana aiki ne game da haɗa kasuwanci da masu hazaƙa ba ne; yana nufin ba wa waɗannan kasuwancin damar ƙimanta basirar da gaske, yana mai tabbatar da dacewa da takamaiman buƙatunsu." Tushen manufar Tech1M ita ce jajircewa don samar da cikakkiyar ƙimanta hazaƙa wanda ya zarce son zuciya kuma yanayi cikin sauri da inganci da kuma gaskiya. Tommie Edwards ta ce "A matsayinmu na kan gaba wajen gina ƙungiyoyin da ake rarrabawa cikin sauri, mai rahusa da inganci, muna da niyyar daidaita wurin aiki, tare da tabbatar da cewa kowane gwani, ba tare da la'akari da wurin da yake ba na da cikakkiyar don isa ga damammakin da suka dace da shi," in ji Tommie Edwards. Duk da kasancewarta sabuwa a kasuwa, manhajar Tech1M ta riga ta samu babban ci gaba na 30% na mako-mako tun lokacin da ta shiga kamfanin Techstars, tare da masu amfani sama da 12,000 da ke kan dandali da kuma fiye da masu haɗaka 28 tare da kasuwanci. Ƙari kan ƙaddamar da samfurinsa mai ban sha'awa, masu hazaƙa sana'a an ba su dama don samun kyaututtuka na tsabar kuɗi da na'urori masu muhimmanci, wanda yake ƙara bayyana jin daɗi a taron. Gidan labarai na Founders Connect Live sun gabatar da batutuwa daban-daban da kuma darussa masu muhimmanci daga fitattun masu ƙirƙira a Najeriya, suna haɓaka yanayi mai dacewa don koyo, haɗin gwiwa, da ƙarfafawa. Abin da ya kamata ku sani game da Manhajar Tech1M Tech1M babbar manhaja ce ta kasuwanci wacce ke ba wa manajoji masu ɗaukan ma'aikata damar tantancewa da ɗaukan masu aiki da biyan ƙwararru a duniya. Ta hanyar daidaito na AI, da ɗauka na neman ma'aikata, da sauran sabbin fasahohi, tana sauƙaƙa tantance ƙimar basira kuma tana ba da damar biyan kuɗin daga kowace a cikin ƙasashe 120. Manhajar Tech1M ta kawo sauyi ga ɗaukar ma'aikata ta hanyar ƙirƙirar yanayi mai sauƙi wanda ke sauƙaƙe ɗaukar ma'aikata, da sake fasalin, da sake horarwa, da riƙe ƙungiyoyin da aka rarraba. Domin samun ƙarin bayanai game da manhajar Tech1M, zaku iya ziyartar www.tech1m.com
Ayyukan da Babu Kamar sa a Farashinta - Jerin Wayoyin Infinix NOTE 30 na Samun Yabo Tsakanin Kafafen Watsa Labarun Kan Fasaha a Duniya Abubuwan ban mamaki kayan kamfanin Infinix madaidaita sun sami kulawa sosai fiye da yadda aka saba a kasuwa. A kwanakinnan ya fitar da jerin abubuwan da ake tsammani a jerin wayoyin NOTE 30, yana ba matasa masu amfani wani zaɓi na musamman na aiki. Shahararrun kafofin watsa labaru na fasaha sun gudanar da cikakkiyar tantancewa game da jerin, suna mai yaba cajin sauri na 68W mai ban sha'awa, zane mai ban sha'awa, manyan fasalulluka, da kuma farashi mai araha. Bari yanzu mu bincika fahimtar waɗannan ƙwararrun kafofin watsa labarai kuma mu shiga cikin duniyar da ke jan hankalin sabbin jerin wayoyin NOTE 30. Yabon Madalla Shahararren mai tantance fasaha a Burtaniya a SuperSaf yayi nazari sosai akan samfuran uku na jerin wayoyin NOTE 30: NOTE 30 da NOTE 30 5G da kuma NOTE 30 Pro. Lokacin da yake tantance wayar NOTE 30 Pro, wanda ke alfahari da saurin cajin na 68W da kuma damar cajin ba waya ta 15W, dole SuperSaf ya bayyana sha'awar sa. Ya ce, "Ita wayar NOTE 30 Pro wata abu cee mai wuyar gaske a kasuwannin wayoyin hannu na yau, yana ba da caji cikin sauri a farashi madaidaici." Yana da kyau a lura cewa wayar NOTE 30 Pro ita ce wayar farko mai farashinta da ke da fasalin cajin marar waya cikin sauri. Ita kanta wacce tafi sauƙin kuɗi wayar NOTE 30 ta ɗauki hankalin SuperSaf don fa'idodinta na musamman. Ya ƙara da cewa, "Wayar NOTE 30 ta fito fili a ɓangaren waya mai sauƙin kuɗi." Wannan jerin yana ba da fasali na ban mamaki kamar 45W na caji mai sauri, allon na'ura 120Hz mai ƙarfi, da ƙarfin ajiya mai yalwa har zuwa 16GB + 256GB, duk akan farashi mai ban sha'awa. Bugu da ƙari, wayar NOTE 30 5G tana faɗaɗa jerin tare da damar 5G da babbar kyamarar 108MP. SuperSaf ya bayyana ra'ayinsa, yana mai cewa, "Wayar NOTE 30 5G tana ba da mafi kyawun aikin kowace wayar 5G a cikin kewayon farashinta." Kafafen Yaɗa Labarai Na Musamman Suka Bayyana Jerin wayar NOTE 30 yana ba da zaɓi tsakanin gilashin da aka yi sanyi ko kuma ƙarshen fata na faux, ga ƙarin taɓawa mai kyau. Kafofin watsa labarai masu daraja kamar GSMArena sun yaba da burin kamfanin Infinix, yana mai cewa, "A bayyane yake kamfanin Infinix yana da buri kuma yana son wucewa sama da ajinsa, wanda muke godiya." Idan aka zo batun ƙarfin batir, wayar NOTE 30 ta wuce abin da ake tsammani, tana samun sa'o'i 119 a lokacin gwaje-gwajen juriya. GSMArena ta lura, "Hakan ma ya fi abin da muke tsammani daga wannan ƙwaƙwalwar kwamfuta da ƙarfin batiri. Bayanin wayar Note 30 ya yi fice a cikin juriyar ta musamman. ” Ba wai kawai wayar NOTE 30 tana burgewa da rayuwar batir ɗinta ba ne, amma ƙarfin cajinta mai sauri na 45W shima yana sanya ra'ayi mai ɗorewa. Wayar tana da sabbin hanyoyin caji mai sauri ta wane salo ta baya, da tdawowa, da ayyuka masu wayo. Wannan yana haɓaka ƙwarewar caji a yanayi daban-daban. Cajin kewayawa, alal misali, yana ba da caji kai tsaye ga mahaifar wayar, yana rage nauyin batiri da haɓaka aikin wasanni—wani muhimmin fasali ga ƙwararrun yan wasan hannu. GSMArena ta yi tsokaci, "Wannan babban fasali ne, musamman don wasanni sannan yana iya haɓaka tsawon rayuwar batiri." Shahararren marubucin yanar gizo na Amurka SomeGadgetGuy ya gudanar da gwajin ƙwaƙwaf kan ingancin sauti na wayar NOTE 30 Pro tare da kunna JBL a cikin ƙaramin ɗakin kwana. Sakamakon ya kasance mai ban sha'awa, tare da bayyanannen sauti da ƙarancin hayaniya. SomeGadgetGuy ya kammala da cewa, "Ina nufin, wannan kyakkyawan sauti ne." Mai rubutun ra'ayi na yanar gizon ya kuma bayyana gamsuwa da allon wayar, wanda ke ba da gyare-gyaren daidaitawa tsakanin 60Hz, 90Hz, da 120Hz, yana mai imani cewa wayar na sadar da ƙwarewa mai kyau ga masu amfani. Ta samu karɓuwa a wurin masu tasiri Shafukan yanar gizo masu tasiri na fasaha na duniya, 9to5Google da GizChina, sun yaba da ingancin farashi na jerin wayoyin NOTE 30. 9to5Google ya bayyana cewa wayar NOTE 30 5G ta zarce sauran zaɓuɓɓuka a cikin kewayon farashinta, tana ba da ingantaccen ƙwarewar mai amfani a Amurka. GizChina ya bawa wayar NOTE 30 Pro babban maki na 4.4, yana mai bayyana ta a matsayin "WAYAR DA TA LASHE VFM BA HAMAYYA." Dukan tantancewar sun yaba da keɓaɓɓen ƙirar, aiki mai ƙarfi, ingancin allo mai ban sha'awa, da cikakkiyar fasahar caji mai sauri na wayar NOTE 30 Pro. Gabaɗaya, kafofin watsa labaru na fasaha sun ba da babbar lambar yabo a kan jerin wayoyin Infinix NOTE 30, tare da amincewa da ƙwarewar aikinta da gogewa a farashi mai araha. An yaba wa jerin wayoyin don ƙimarsa na musamman. Wannan yana ƙarfafa imaninmu cewa sabon-sabon jerin wayoyin NOTE 30 zai mamaye kasuwar waya mai rahusa a ƙarshen rabin shekara. Kamfanin Infinix yana nufin kawo farin cikin fasaha ga mutane da yawa a duk duniya tare da wayar NOTE 30 da na'urorin Infinix na gaba a shirye don ƙara ƙarfafa matasa na yau da gobe.
Makarantar i-Academy tana ba da Hazaƙar Fasaha kuma tana Bukin Nasarar Hackathon Makarantar i-Academy, babban shirin koyar da ilimin fasaha wanda Africa Prudential Plc ke tallafawa, yana ci gaba da samun gagarumar nasara wajen samar da damammaki na ci gaba da wayewa a masana'antar fasaha. Tare da jajircewarta na rage tasirin hazaƙar fasaha, makarantar i-Academy tana ba da cikakkiyar horo na watanni tara da aka tsara don bawa matasa masu sha'awar fannin fasaha da ƙwarewa da ilimin da suka dace don kasancewa a shirye don aiki, tare da yin fice a fanni fasaha da koyaushe ke ƙara faɗaɗa. Shirin horo na i-Academy ya ƙunshi ƙirƙirar manhaja ta gaba da ta baya, wanda aka tsara tare da muhimman horon fasaha mai sauƙi. Ta hanyar tsarin ilmantarwa a gauraye, ɗalibai suna samun ƙwarewa ta hannu da kuma wayewa da ayyukan rayuwa na zahiri, suna tabbatar da cewa sun shirya sosai don buƙatun masana'antu bayan kammala karatun. A wani ɓangare ƙoƙarinta na haɓaka sabbin abubuwa da haɗin gwiwa, kwanannan i-Academy ta karɓi gagarumin gasar hackathon cikin nasara, wanda ke bayyana jimlar ƙungiyoyi tara. Taron ya samar da dandali ga ƙungiyoyi don nuna aikace-aikacen ilimin da suka samu, da nuna gwanintarsu, da kuma baje kolin ƙwarewar warware matsalolinsu na musamman. A cikin rukunonin da suka halarci gasar, rukuni na 3 ne wanda ya ƙunshi ƙwararrun mutane huɗu ne suka bayyana a matsayin ƙungiyar da ta yi nasara, inda suka samu kyautar kuɗi na NGN 150,000. Ma'aunin shari'a don gasar sun ƙunshi nau'o'i daban-daban, ciki har da ƙirƙira da dabaru, da ƙwarewar fasaha, da iya warware matsaloli, da haɗin gwiwa da haɗin gwiwar aiki, ingancin lambar, ƙwarewar mai amfani da tsari, da tasiri da salon karɓar canji, da gabatarwa da iya sadarwa, da kuma la'akari da ɗabi'a. Ana buƙatar kowane rukuni ya gabatar da cikakken bayani game da aikinsu, yana nuna bayanin matsalar, da mafita da aka samar, da muhimman fasali da ayyuka, da fasaha da kuma kayan aikin da aka yi amfani da su. Kwamitin alƙalai masu daraja, wanda ya ƙunshi Antoinette Edodo; Shugaban canjin kasuwanci na Africa Prudential Plc, Osahon Elaiho; Shugaban Kamfanin Injiniya na Afirka Prudential Plc, Olusegun Adesina; shi Audit Analyst Africa Prudential Plc, Roy Anaedobe; Jagoran Manazarcin Kasuwancin Afirka Prudential Plc, da Phillip Nkwam Analytics & ML Leader The Bulb Africa, sun gamsu da yadda dukkan rukunin da suka halarci taron suka nuna sha'awarsu sosai. Sun ba da ra'ayi mai ƙima ga kowane rukuni, suna ba da haske da shawarwari don haɓaka Mafi ƙarancin Muhimman Kayayyakin (MVPs) da ƙara haɓaka ayyukansu. Kalli wannan fili don ƙarin bayani game da samfuransu, waɗanda za mu raba tare da zaɓin rukuni. Ivy Ikpeme-Mbakwem, Daraktan Tsare-tsare na i-Academy ya ce "Muna matuƙar alfahari da nasarorin Rukuni na 3 da kuma dukkan mahalarta taron gasar.". “Sadaukarwarsu da ƙirƙira, da ruhin haɗin kai suna misalta halayen da muke ƙoƙarin ɗora wa ɗalibanmu. Makarantar i-Academy ta ci gaba da jajircewa wajen rayawa da ƙarfafawa yara da zasu zama manyan gobe ta hanhyar samun ilimimummuka ta ɓangarori da dama na fasaha masu inganci, da samar da tasiri mai kyau a cikin tsarin fasahar Najeriya." Ta hanyar manya-manyan shirye-shiryenta na horarwa da himma kamar gasar nan, i-Academy na ci gaba da tsara kyakkyawar makoma ga masana'antar fasaha, tana mai ba da ƙwarewa da ake buƙata da tallafi ga masu sha'awar fasaha. Domin samun ƙarin bayani game da i-Academy da shirye-shiryenta, da fatan zaku ziyarci https://t.me/iacademy23 Game da i-Academy: i-Academy, wanda Africa Prudential Plc ke tallafawa, shiri ne na ilimi da zamantakewa da tattalin arziki da aka sadaukar don magance ƙarancin ƙwararru a fannin fasaha a Najeriya da sauran su. Ta hanyar manya-manyan shirinta na horarwa na watanni tara, i-Academy tana bawa matasa masu sha'awar fasaha tare da muhimman ƙwarewa da ilimin da ake buƙata don bunƙasa a cikin masana'antar fasaha. Shirin na nufin samar da damammaki don haɓakawa da ci gaba yayin da ake haɓaka al'adun ƙirƙira da haɗin gwiwa.
InDrive ta sanar da tsawaita SamfurinFaɗi-abin da-zaka biya zuwa ƙarin biranen Najeriya 15 tare da ƙaddamar da sabbin ayyukan jigilar kayayyaki. Ƙarfafa Ayyuka ba tare bawa Hukuma Sisi ba don Direbobi a cikin Sabbin Birane 15 A ranar Juma’a, 14 ga watan Yuli, inDrive, dandalin zirga-zirgar jama'a da sabis na birane a duniya, ya bayyana shirye-shiryen tsawaita sabis ɗin yawo tsakanin abokan tafiya zuwa sabbin biranen Najeriya 15 da kuma ƙaddamar da samfurin jigilar kaya mai suna, inDrive.Freight. An sanar da hakan ne a makon Sabbin kamfanoni na Legas 2023, wanda ke bikin kasuwanci da ƙirƙire-ƙirƙire a Afirka. Timothy Oladimeji, Wakilin Ci Gaban Kasuwanci, inDrive Nigeria, ya bayyana hada-hada a matsayin ainihin buƙatun da kowane ɗan adam dole ne ya kasance kuma ya jaddada haɓakar birni 15 ta hanyar inDrive ya sa wannan ya zama mai sauƙi ga kowa da kowa a cikin al'ummomin gida ta hanyar daidaitattun sauƙin samfurin abin hawa. Da yake magana game da ƙaddamar da samfurin tallafi na kayan aiki ga ƙananan, da matsakaita, da kuma manyan masana'antu, Oladimeji ya ce, "Daga bayanan da aka bincika, mun gane cewa mutane suna son sabis na jigilar kaya wanda zai iya taimaka musu wajen jigilar mai nauyi fiye da 20kg. Don haka, mun gabatar da ingantaccen tsarin sabis ɗinmu - inDrive.Freight - sabis na isar da buƙatu na yau da kullun wanda ke bawa abokan cinikinmu da sauran masu kasuwanci damar jigilar kayayyaki masu nauyi 20kg zuwa 20tn, ba tare da matsala ba.” Wakilin Ci gaban Kasuwancin ya ci gaba da bayyana cewa samfurin inDrive.Freight yana nuna manhajar abubuwa masu sauƙi, wanda zai bawa abokan ciniki damar saita farashin da aka fi so, zaɓar motoci, da zaɓar direbobi. Har ila yau, yana nuna wani nau'i na musamman wanda ke bawa abokan ciniki damar sanin kayan da suke son aikawa. Ga masu kasuwanci, wannan yana da tasiri mai canjawa kamar yadda masu kasuwancin ba za su ƙara saka jari ba don kafa sabis na jigilar kayayyaki ko haɗin gwiwar kasuwancin dabaru kai kaya, tare da hanyoyin rage kuɗi da aka bayar ta hanyar amfani da inDrive.Freight. A ci gaba da ƙaddamar da shirin a fadin Najeriya, a ranar Litinin, 18 ga watan Yuli, an fara faɗaɗa aikin inDrive zuwa sabbin garuruwa 15 a Najeriya a hukumance.
